hadiths[177]{hadithnumber,text}:
4596,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' yahudi ikahattar ya bahattar firqon mein taqseem huey aur esaai bhi ikahattar ya bahattar firqon mein batey aur meri ummat tihattar firqon mein taqseem hogi .''"
4597,abu-Aamir Hozani ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Muawiya bin abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu Anhuma) ham mein khutba deney ke liye khadey huey aur kaha : khabrdar ! tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham mein khadey huey aur farmaya : '' khabrdar ! tum se pehley ehle-kitab 72 firqon mein taqseem huey they aur ye millat 73 firqon mein taqseem hogi. 72 aag mein jaeyngey aur eik firqa jannat mein jaeyga aur yehi ''al-Jamaat'' hoga .''ibne-Yahya aur Amr ne apni riwaayaton mein mazeed kaha : ''bila-shuba meri ummat mein se kuch qomen niklengi un mein ye ahwaa (man pasand nazariyat aur aamaal ko deen mein dakhil karna) aisey saraayat kar jaeyngi jaisey ke baawlepan ki bimari apney bimar mein saraayat kar jati hai.'' Amr ne kaha : '' baawle pan ke bimar ki koi rag aur koi jod baqi nahin rehta jis mein us bimari ka asar na ho.''
4598,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat kareema tilawat farmaai هو الذي أنزل عليك الكتاب منه آيات محكمات . . تا . . أولوا الألباب  ( Allah ( wo zaat hai jisney aap par kitab nazil ki, jis mein baaz aayaten mohkam ( wazeh ( hain jo is kitab ki asal buniyad hain aur kuch dusri aayaten mutshabihaat ( ghair wazeh ( hain, to jinkey dilon mein tedh hai wo un mein se unhi aayaton ke peechey padey rehtey hain jo mutashabeh ( ghair wazeh ( hain, unka maqsad mehaz fitney aur taaweel ki talash hota hai, halanke Allah ke siwa koi bhi unki taaweel nahin janta , aur jo log pukhta ilm waley hain wo kehtey hain ke hamara in ( mutshabihaat ( par emaan hai, ye sab hamarey rab ki taraf se hain aur nasihat wohi log pakadtey hain jo aql waley hain.'' Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum aisey logon ko dekho jo mutashabeh aayaton ke peechey padtey hon to ye wohi log hain jinkey baarey mein Allah ne farmaya hai : ( فاحذروهم ( '' un se dartey aur bachtey raho .''"
4599,"Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aamaal mein se afzal amal Allah ke liye mohabbat karna aur usi ke liye bughz rakhna hai.''"
4600,"Janab Abdullah apney walid Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke na-bina ho janey ke baad unke qed hua kartey they. wo bayan kartey hain ke maine ( apney walid ( Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna . . . . aur ibn sarah ne unke ghazwa tabuk mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se peechey reh janey ka qissa bayan kya. . . . kaha ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musalmanon ko ham teeno se baat cheet se mana farma diya. yahan tak ke jab ye soorat haal mujh par bahut taweel (aur giraan (ho gaee to maine abu-Qatada ke baagh ki deewar par chadh kar us se baat ki, wo merey chacha ka beta tha, maine salam kya to Allah ki qasam ! usney merey salam ka jawab nahin diya. phir ( ibn sarah ne ( unki tauba nazil honey ki khabar bayan ki ."
4601,Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main apney ghar walon ke paas pahuncha aur haalat ye thi ke merey haath phat gaey they. to unhoney mujhey ( merey haathon par) Zaafran laga diya. subh ke waqt mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur maine salam arz kya to aapney mujhey jawab na diya aur farmaya : '' jao usey dho dalo .''
4602,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke ummul-momenin Safiya binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anha) ka oont bimar ho gaya aur ummul-momenin Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ke paas eik zayed sawari thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se kaha : '' oont usey dey do .'' to unhoney kaha : bhala mein us yahoodan ko dun? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghussa ho gaey aur zul-hijja , Moharram aur safar ke kuch dino tak un se baat cheet na ki ."
4603,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Quran karim mein jhagda karna kufr hai.''"
4604,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabrdar ! mujhey Quran ke sath us jaisi eik aur chiz bhi di gaee hai. an-qareeb aisey hoga ke eik pet bhara ( aasooda haal ( aadmi apney takht ya diwan par betha kahega ke usi Quran ko ikhtiyar kar lo , jo us mein halal hai usey halal jano aur jo us mein haram hai usey haram samjho . khabrdar ! tumharey liye paaltu gadhey , neesh daar darindey aur kisi zimmi ( kafir (ka gira pada maal utha lena halal nahin, siwaey iske ke uska Malik us se be parwa ho. aur jo koi kisi qom ke paas jaey to un par wajib hai ke uski mehmani karen, agar wo uski mehmani na keren to usey haq hasil hai ke apni mehmani ke misl un se bazariey taqat hasil kar ley.''"
4605,"Janab Ubaidullah apney walid Hazrat abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hergiz aisa na ho ke main tum mein se kisi ko paaun ke wo apney takht ya diiwaan par betha ho aur uskey paas merey ehkam mein se koi hukm pahunchey jis ka maine hukm diya ho ya us se mana kya ho to wo kehney lagey ke ham nahin jantey , ham to kitabullah mein jo paeyngey, usi par amal karengey .''"
4606,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney hamarey us maamley ( deen ( mein koi naee chiz paida ki jo us mein se nahin to wo mardud aur batil hai. ibn Esa ne yun riwayat kya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney hamarey tareeqey ke khilaf koi kaam kya to wo mardud aur batil hai.''"
4607,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Amr Salma aur Hajar bin Hajar ka bayan hai ke ham Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey jinkey baarey mein ye aayat kareema nazil hui thi : ولا على الذين إذا ما أتوك '' un logon par koi gunah nahin ke jab wo aap ke paas aaye ke aap unhen sawari den , aapney kaha ke merey paas koi chiz nahin, to wo us haal mein lot gaey ke unki aankhen , is gham se aansu baha rahi thin ke unhen kuch muyassar nahin jisey wo kharch keren .'' ham ne unhen salam kya aur arz kya : ham aap se milney ke liye aaye hain aur ye ke aap ki iyaadat ho jaey aur koi ilmi faeyda bhi hasil kar lein , to Hazrat Irbaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen eik din Namaz padhaai , phir hamari taraf munh kar liya aur waaz farmaya , bada hi baleegh aur Jaame waaz , aisa ke us se hamari aankhen beh padin aur dil dahal gaey . eik kehney waley ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye to maano alwadaai waaz tha, to aap hamen kya wasiyat farmatey hain? farmaya : ''main tumhen wasiyat karta hun ke Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar kiye rehna aur apney hukkaam ke ehkam sunna aur manna , chahe koi Habshi ghulam hi kyon na ho. bila-shuba tum mein se jo merey baad zinda raha wo bahut ikhtilaf dekhega , chunanche un halaat mein meri sunnat aur merey khulafa ki sunnat apnaey rakhna , khulafa jo as-haabe-rushad w hidayat hain, sunnat ko khoob mazboot se thaamna , balke daadhiyon se pakdey rehna , naee naee bidaat se apney aap ko bachaey rakhna , bila-shuba her naee baat bidat hai aur her bidat gumrahi hai.''"
4608,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabrdar ! had se badhney waley halak huey .'' aapney ye baat teen baar farmaey."
4609,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo raahe-haq ki dawat dey usey is qadr sawab hai jis qadr uski ittiba kerney walon ko hoga. un ittiba kerney walon mein se kisi ke sawab mein koi kami nahin hogi. aur jisney kisi gumrahi ki dawat di to usey usi qadr gunah hoga jis qadr uski perwi kerney walon ko hoga. is wajeh se unke gunahon mein koi kami na hogi .''"
4610,"Janab Aamir bin Saad apney walid (Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalmanon mein jurm ke aetbar se sab se bada ( mujrim ( wo musalman hai jisney kisi aisi baat ke baarey mein sawal kya jo pehley haram na thi , magar uskey sawal kerney ke baais haram kar di gaee .''"
4611,"Yazid bin Umaira Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal ke sathiyon mein se they. unhoney bataya ke Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) jab bhi zikr ki majlis mein bethtey to unki zaban se ye alfaz nikaltey : Allah azz-w-jall khoob aadil aur faisla kerney wala hai, shak kerney waley halak ho gaey . Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne eik din kaha : tumharey baad badey fitney hongey . maal bahut badh jaeyga aur Quran khol ( aam kar) diya jaeyga yahan tak ke momin , munafiq , mard , aurten , chhota , bada , ghulam aur azad sabhi usey hasil karengey aur aisa hoga ke kehney wala kahega : logon ko kya hua meri perwi nahin kartey , halanke maine Quran padha hai? ( wo kahega ( ye log us waqt tak meri perwi nahin karengey yahan tak ke main unke liye uskey ilawa koi naee ikhtiraa'a karun. chunanche tum apney aap ko uski bidat se bachaey rakhna , uski bidat zalalat aur gumrahi hogi . aur main tumhen daana bandey ki thokar se bhi darata hun. shetan kabhi daana bandey ki zaban se gumrahi ka koi kalma niklwa deta hai aur kabhi munafiq bhi haq baat keh deta hai. ( Yazid kehtey hain ( maine Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : Allah aap par rehem farmaai ! mujhey kaisey maloom ho ke daana aadmi gumrahi ka kalma keh jata hai aur munafiq haq ki baat keh deta hai? kaha ke haan . daana ki aisi baaton se bachna jo mashhoor ho jati hain, jinkey baarey mein kaha jata hai ke ye kya hai? magar ye baat tumhara us se rukh mod leney ka baais na baney , aisa ( bhi to (ho sakta hai ke wo us se ruju kar ley , aur haq jis kisi se bhi suno qubul kar lo , bila-shuba haq par Noor hota hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Maamer ne Zohri ke wastey us riwayat mein) يثنينك ( ki bajaey ( وَلَا يُنْئِيَنَّكَ ذَلِكَ عَنْهُ ( ''ye baat tujhey us se be rukh na bana dey .'' ke lafz riwayat kiye hain. saleh bin kaisaan ne Zohri se riwayat kartey huey ( mushtahiraat ( ki bajaey ( المشتبهات (ka lafz riwayat kya aur aisey hi ( la يثنينك (ka lafz riwayat kya jaisey ke Aqeel ne riwayat kya hai. ibn Is-haq ne Zohri se riwayat kartey huey kaha : haan daana ki jo baat tumharey liye shubhe ka baais ho yahan tak ke tum kehney lago naa-maaloom usney us kalma se kya murad liya hai?"
4612,"abu-Rijaa ne abu Salat se riwayat kya ke eik shakhs ne Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ko khat likha . jis mein usney un se taqdir ka masla daryaft kya, to unhoney jawab likha : hamd w salat ke baad, main tumhen wasiyat karta hun ke Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar kiye raho aur Allah ke Amr mein aetidaal se kaam lo. Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat ka ittiba karo aur bidaton ki bad-duaa se door raho bil-khusus jab deen ke maamley mein aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sunnat jari ho chuki aur us mein logon ki zarurat puri ho chuki . sunnat ko lazim pakdo yaqinan yehi chiz Allah ki marzi sey tumharey liye ( gumrahi sey) bachney ka sabab hogi . yaad rakho ! logon ne jis qadr bhi bad-dua nikali hain, un se pehley wo rehnumai aa chuki jo un ( bad-duaa (ke khilaf daleel hai. ya us mein koi na koi ibrat hai. bila-shuba sunnat us muqaddas zaat ne ata farmaai jinhen ilm tha ke uski mukhalifat mein kya. . . . raawi Muhammad bin kaseer ne (من قد علم) ke lafz riwayat nahin kiye. . . . khata thokar aur himaqat aur) halakat ki) khai hai. lihaza apney aap ko us chiz par razi aur mutmain rakho jis par qom ( Sahaba ( razi rahey hain, bila-shuba wo log ilm se behrawar they. ( jin baaton se unhoney mana kya ( gehri baseerat ki bina par mana kya aur un haqaeeq ki aagahi par (jin se tum b-zoam khuwesh aagah huey ho ( wo log ziyada qadir they aur apney fazaail ki bina par uskey ziyada haqdaar they. agar haq w hidayat yehi hai jisey tum ne samjha hai to tum goya un se sabqat ley gaey . agar tum ye kaho ke ye umur (batein) un ( Sahaba (ke baad naey ejaad huey hain to unke ejaad kerney waley un ( Sahaba ( ki raah par nahin hain, balke un se aeraz kerney waley hain. bila-shuba wo Sahaba hi ( haq aur neki mein) sabqat ley janey waley they. unhoney un umur (baton) mein jo baat ki wohi kafi hai. jo bayan kya usi mein shifa hai. chunanche un se kam tar par rukna kotahi ( tafrit ( hai aur un se badh kar tauzeeh karna ziyadti ya thakawat ( ifraat ( hai) unke tarz amal se kami karna jayez hai, na un se badhna jayez ( jinhon ne kami ki unhoney zulm kya aur jo aagey badhey unhoney ghulw kya. jabkey wo ( Sahaba ( unke darmyan ( asal ( hidayat aur seedhi raah par they. tum ne taqdir ke iqrar ke mutalliq likh kar puchha hai tu Allah ke fazal se tum ne eik sahibe-ilm w khabar se puchha hai. main nahin janta ke logon ne jitni bhi naee baaten ghadi hain aur jitni bhi bad-duaa ejaad ki hain un mein taqdir ke masley se badh kar bhi koi masla wazeh aur dalaeel ki ro se qawi tar ho, uska zikr to qadim tareen jahiliyat key dinon mein bhi hota tha, log apni guftgu aur apney ashaar mein uska zikr kartey they, jo chiz unhen hasil na ho paati thi , taqdir ka zikr karkey us se tasalli paatey they. phir Islam ne unke baad mein aqeeda taqdir ko mazeed ( wazeh aur) mazboot kya hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik do nahin, mutaaddid ahadis mein uska zikr kya hai. musalmanon ne aap se sun kar aap ki zindagi mein aur aap ke baad bhi uskey baarey mein guftgu ki . jis mein Allah ke samney tasleem w raza aur apney ijz ka aetraaf kya ke koi chiz aisi nahin jis par Allah ka ilm muheet na ho, ya kitab taqdir mein uska shumar na ho, ya us mein uski taqdir jari na hui ho. sath hi ye baat uski mohkam kitab ( Quran hakim ( mein bhi hai. Sahaba kiram ne us masley ko usi se akhaz kya tha aur yahin se wo us se ba-khabar huey . agar tum kaho Allah ne falan aayat kyon nazil ki aur is tarah kyon kaha ? to ( zara socho ke) unhon (yani Sahaba ( ne bhi to yehi aayaat padhein jo tum ne padhein . albatta wo uski tafseer w taaweel pa gaey jis se tum jahil rahey . uskey baad unka qol ye hai ke ye sab Allah ki taraf se likha hua aur uski taqdir se hai. shaqaawat aur bad-bakhti bhi likhi hui hai. jo kuch muqaddar hai, ho jata hai. Allah jo bhi chahta hai hota hai aur jo nahin chahta nahin hota . ham apney nafa aur nuqsan ke Malik nahin hain. phir ( usi asal par) wo Allah ki taraf raaghib rahey aur usi se dartey rahey ."
4613,"Janab Naafe bayan kartey hain ke shaam mein Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka eik dost tha, jiski un se khat kitaabat rehti thi. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko likha : mujhey ye khabar pahunchi hai ke to ney taqdir ke baarey mein koi baaten ki hain. ( to taqdir ko jhutlata hai) lihaza aainda ke liye mujhey koi khat na likhna . bila-shuba maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : '' tehqiq meri ummat mein aisey log paida hongey jo taqdir ko jhutlayengey .''"
4614,"Janab Khalid haza (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Janab Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) se kaha : abu-Saeed! mujhey ye bataeyn ke Hazrat Adam Alehissalam aasman ke liye paida kiye gaey they ya zameen ke liye? unhoney kaha : zameen ke liye. maine kaha : kya khayal hai agar wo gunah se bach jatey aur darkht se na khatey to . . . . ? kaha : ye unke liye mumkin hi na tha ( kyonkey yehi muqaddar tha. ( maine kaha Allah taala ke us farman ka kya mafhoom hai : ( jo jinnat aur shayateen ke mutalliq farmaya : ) ما أَنْتُمْ عَلَيْهِ بِفَاتِنِينَ . إِلَّا من هُوَ صَالِ الْجَحِيمِ ''tum kisi ko Allah ki taraf se nahin pher ( behka ( saktey ho, magar usey hi jo jahannam mein padney wala ho.'' ( kaha ke shayateen apni gumrahi se sirf unhi ko gumrah kartey hain jin par Allah ne jahannam mein girna wajib kya ho."
4615,Janab Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) se manqul hai ke unhoney Allah taala ke us farman : ( ولذلك خلقهم ( ''Allah ne unko isi liye paida kya (ke haq se ikhtilaf kartey rahen.'' ( ki tafseer mein farmaya ke un logon ko us ( jahannam (ke liye paida kya aur doosron ko is ( jannat (ke liye.
4616,Khalid haza kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) se aayat kareema : ( ما أَنْتُمْ عَلَيْهِ بِفَاتِنِينَ . إِلَّا من هُوَ صَالِ الْجَحِيمِ ( ki tafseer (ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya ke ye Allah taala ne usi ke liye lazim kya hai jo jahannam mein jalney wala hua . (ye mazkura baala riwayat 4614 ki manind hai. (
4617,Janab Humaid se manqul hai ke Hazrat Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) kaha kartey they ke aasman se zameen par gir padna mujhey us se ziyada pasand hai ke main yun kahun ke maamla merey haath mein hai. (maqsad ye hai ke taqdir ka inkar mujhey hergiz hergiz gawara nahin.)
4618,Janab Humaid ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) Makka aaye to wahan ke ulama w fuqaha ne mujh se kaha ke main un se ye kahun ke wo eik din hamen waaz sunaeyn . to unhoney qubul kar liya . chunanche wo jama ho gaey aur Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) ne dars diya to maine un se badh kar kisi ko khateeb na paya . eik aadmi ne puchha : abu-Saeed ! shetan ko kis ne paida kya hai? wo kehney lagey Subhanallah ! bhala Allah ke siwa bhi koi khaliq hai? Allah hi ne shetan ko paida kya hai. khair aur shar ka khaliq wohi hai. to wo aadmi kehney laga : Allah unko halak karey (na-maaloom) kis bina par wo us Shekh par jhoot boltey hain.
4619,Janab Humaid Taweel ne Hazrat Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) se riwayat kya ke unhoney is aayat kareema ( كذلك نسلكه في قلوب المجرمين ( '' aisey hi ham ye baat mujrimon ke dilon mein dal detey hain.'' ki tafseer mein kaha : us se murad '' shirk '' hai.
4620,"Ubaid al Seid, Hazrat Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) se riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney aayat kareema ( وحيل بينهم وبين ما يشتهون ( ki tafseer mein kaha ke unke aur unke emaan laney ki khahish mein rukawat kar di jaeygi ."
4621,Janab ibn Aun kehtey hain ke main mulk shaam mein tha ke peechey se kisi ne mujh ko aawaz di. main mutawajjeh hua to dekha ke Janab Rija bin hewa they. unhoney kaha : abu-Aaun ! ye kya baaten hain jo log Hasan Basri ke mutalliq keh rahey hain? maine kaha : ye log Hasan par bahut jhoot bol rahey hain.
4622,"Ayub ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) par jhoot bolney waley do tarah ke log hain. eik wo jo taqdir ke munkir hain. unki khahish hai ke is tarah se apni baat aur raey ko shohrat de lein aur aam kar den. aur doosrey wo hain jinkey dilon mein bughz aur adawat hai (aur is tarah baaten kartey hain ( kya ye uska qol nahin, kya usney is tarah nahin kaha hai? waghera ."
4623,Janab Qurra bin Khalid ham se kaha kartey they aey jawaano! Hasan Basri ke baarey mein maghloob na ho jana. bila-shuba unki raey sunnat ke mutabiq aur haq w sawaab (ke tabey) thi.
4624,"ibne-Aun ne kaha : agar hamen ye ilm hota ke Hasan Basri ki kahi hui baat is had tak pahunch jaeygi jahan tak ke pahunchi to ham unke ruju ke mutalliq eik kitab likhtey aur us par gawahi qaaim kartey. lekin ham samjhey ke eik baat thi jo ho gaee so ho gaee, mashhoor na hogi."
4625,Ayub kehtey hain ke Janab Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) ne mujh se kaha : main aainda kabhi aisi baat nahin kahunga .) jis mein taqdir ke inkar ka shubha ho. (
4626,Usman al batti bayan kartey hain ke Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) ne jab bhi) Quran karim ki) kisi aayat ki tafseer ki to us mein taqdir ke asbaat (aur us par emaan ( hi ka zikr kya.
4627,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein ham Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke barabar kisi ko na kartey they. phir unke baad Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke baad Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) ka darja samajhtey they ( phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab mein koi tafzeel na samajhtey they ( balke sab ko barabar samajhtey they. (
4628,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke ham kaha kartey they jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hayaat they : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat mein aap ke baad sab se afzal abu-Bakar hain, phir umr aur phir Usman . Allah un sab se razi ho."
4629,"( Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke farzand arjumand ( Janab Muhammad bin Hanfiya se marwi (bayan) hai kehtey hain ke main apney walid se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baad sab se afzal kon hai? unhoney kaha : Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) . maine kaha : phir kon? kaha Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) . phir mujhey andesha hua ke agar maine poochh liya ke unke baad kon hai, to wo kahengaey Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) . to maine khud se keh diya : phir to ‎ aap hongey, abba jaan ! wo kehney lagey : main to musalmanon mein se eik aam aadmi hun."
4630,"Janab Sufiyan Sauri (Rahimahullah) kaha kartey they : jis shakhs ka ye guman ho ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) , Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki nisbat khilaafat ke ziyada haqdaar they to usney Hazrat abu-Bakar , Hazrat umr , muhajrin aur ansaar (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ko ghalati par samjha . aur main nahin samajhta ke us aqeeda ke hotey huey uska koi amal aasman ki taraf uthta ho."
4631,"Janab Sufiyan Sauri (Rahimahullah) kaha kartey they ke khulafa paanch hain. yani abu-Bakar, Umar, Usman, Ali aur umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ."
4632,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : maine aaj raat khuwab mein dekha hai ke eik badal se ghi aur shehad tapak raha hai. maine logon ko dekha ke wo apni hatheliyan phelaey huey they, to kuch ne un se khoob khoob liya aur kuch ne kam liya . aur maine eik rassi dekhi jo aasman se zameen tak latki hui hai, aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap ko dekha ke aapney usko pakda hai aur ooper chadh gaey hain. phir eik doosrey aadmi ne usey pakda wo bhi ooper chadh gaya. phir eik aur aadmi ne usey pakda aur ooper chadh gaya. phir eik aur aadmi ne pakda to wo toot gaee . phir jod di gaee to wo ooper chadh gaya. pas Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : merey maa baap aap par qurban ! mujhey ijazat diijiye ke main uski tabeer arz karun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski tabeer bayan karo.'' to unhoney kaha : wo badal , Islam ka saya hai aur us se tapakney wala ghi aur shehad , Quran ki mulaaimiyat aur sheerni hai. ziyada ya kam leney waley, to wo wohi hain jo Quran se apna hissey ziyada ley rahey hain ya kam . aur aasman se latakney wali rassi , wohi haq hai jis par aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain. aapney usey pakda hai tu Allah aap ko buland farmaeyga . phir aap ke baad eik aadmi pakdega aur uskey zariey se ooper chadh jaeyga. uskey baad doosra aadmi pakdega to wo bhi ooper chadh jaeyga . phir teesra aadmi pakdega to wo toot jaeygi, phir usey uski khatir jod diya jaeyga to phir wo ooper chadh jaeyga . aey Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! mujhey zarur bataeyn ke maine durust kaha hai ya ghalat? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kuch durust kaha hai aur kuch mein ghalati ki hai.'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main aap ko qasam de-kar kehta hun mujhey zarur bataeyn ke maine kya ghalati ki hai. aapney farmaya: '' qasam mat do.''"
4633,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye mazkura baala qissa bayan kya, kaha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( ghalati ki wazahat kerney sey) inkar farma diya."
4634,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik din daryaft farmaya : ''tum mein se khuwab kis ne dekha hai?'' eik aadmi ne kaha : maine . maine dekha ke goya aasman se eik tarazu utri hai to aapka aur Hazrat abu-Bakar ka wazan kya gaya to aap Hazrat abu-Bakar se bhari ho gaey. phir Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr ka wazan kya gaya to abu-Bakar bhari ho gaey . aur Hazrat umr aur Hazrat Usman ka wazan kya gaya to Hazrat umr bhari ho gaey, phir tarazu utha li gaee . to (us baat par) ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chehra aqdas par naa-pasandidgi ke aasaar dekhay .''"
4635,Janab Abdur-Rehman apney walid abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik din daryaft farmaya : ''tum mein se kisi ne khuwab dekha hai? '' to mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kya. magar us riwayat mein) كراهية (ka zikr nahin. balke (فاستاء لها رسول الله ﷺ) yani aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye ( keyfiyat ( pasand na aai . phir farmaya : ''ye nabuwat ki khilaafat hai. phir uskey baad Allah jisey chahega apna mulk inayat farma dega .''
4636,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kya kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aaj raat eik nek bandey ko khuwab dikhaya gaya hai ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath muallaq kya gaya hai aur Hazrat umr ko Hazrat abu-Bakar ke sath muallaq kya gaya hai aur Hazrat Usman ko Hazrat umr ke sath muallaq kya gaya hai.'' Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan se uthey to ham ne kaha : '' saleh aadmi '' to wo khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain aur unka eik doosrey ke sath muallaq karna , isliye ke yehi log us Amr ke zimmedar hain jiskey sath Allah ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Nabi banakar bheja hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke us riwayat ko Yunus aur Shuaib ne riwayat kya hai magar un dono ne sanad mein Amr (bin Aban (ka zikr nahin kya."
4637,"Hazrat Samra bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine dekha hai jaisey eik dol aasman se latkaayaa gaya , to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaye hain aur usko uskey dono taraf ke kinaron se pakad liya . aur us se pani piya , magar kamzori ke sath . phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) aaye unhoney usko uskey dono kinaron se pakda aur piya aur khoob sair ho kar pet bhar kar piya . phir Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) aaye , unhoney uskey dono kinaron se pakda aur piya yahan tak ke pet bhar kar piya . phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aaye , unhoney uskey dono kinaron se pakda to wo hila aur us se kuch pani un par gir gaya."
4638,"Janab Mak-hool (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : zarur aisa hoga ke Rumi log chaalis din tak Shaamiyon ke gharon mein ghusey rahengey . us ( fitney ( se siwaye dimashq aur amaan ka koi shehar na bachega ."
4639,Janab Abu-Aayas Abdur-Rehman bin Salman (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey they ke eik ajmi badshah sarey shehron par ghalib aa jaeyga aur sirf dimashq mehfooz rahega .
4640,Janab Mak-hool (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jangon (aur fitnon (ke dino mein musalman eik aisi jagah khema zan hongey jisey ghota kehtey hongey .''
4641,"Auf (bin abi Jameela Erab ( ne bayan kya, unhoney kaha : maine Hajjaj (bin Yusuf ( ko khutba detey huey suna, wo keh raha tha ke Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki misal Allah ke yahan Esa ibn Maryam ki tarah hai. phir ye aayat padhi : ( { إِذْ قَالَ اللَّهُ يَا عِيسَى إِنِّي مُتَوَفِّيكَ وَرَافِعُكَ إِلَيَّ وَمُطَهِّرُكَ مِنْ الَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا } ( ''jab Allah taala ne farmaya : aey Esa ! main tumhen (is jahan sey) pura pura ley janey wala hun aur apni taraf utha leney wala hun aur un kafiron ki sohbat se tumhen paak kerney wala hun.'' wo ye aayat padhta jata tha aur uski sharah kartey huey apney haath se hamari taraf aur ahle-Sham ki taraf isharay karta jata tha."
4642,"Rabeea bin Khalid zabi ne bayan kya ke maine Hajjaj (bin Yusuf ( ko khutba detey huey suna, usney apney khutbey mein kaha : ham mein se kisi ka qaasid jo uskey kisi kaam mein mashghool ho, wo uskey liye ziyada mohtaram hota hai ya uska wo naaib jo uskey ehle mein thehra hua ho? pas maine apney dil mein kaha : mujh par Allah ke liye ye nazar hai ke ab terey peechey kabhi Namaz nahin padhunga , aur agar mujhey kuch log mil gaey jo terey khilaf jihad kartey hon to main unke sath mil kar bil-zaroor jihad karunga . Is-haq ne apni riwayat mein mazeed kaha : chunanche usney ( Rabeea bin Khalid ne Hajjaj ke khilaf der ( jamajam ke qitaal mein hissey liya yahan tak ke qatl ho gaya."
4643,"Aasim se marwi (bayan) hai ke maine Hajjaj se suna, wo member par keh raha tha : Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar karo jahan tak himmat pao , us mein koi istisna nahin. ameerul-momeneen Abdul-Malik (bin Marwan ( ki baat suno aur itaat karo, us mein koi istisna nahin. Allah ki qasam ! agar main logon ko hukm dun ke masjid ke falan darwazey se bahir jao aur wo doosrey kisi darwazey se bahir niklen to merey liye unke khoon aur maal halal hongey . Allah ki qasam ! agar main Muzar ke badley qabeela Rabeea ki giraft karun to ye merey liye Allah ki taraf se halal hai. aur kon hai jo mujhey Huzail ke ghulam ( ishara hai Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) ki taraf se mazoor janey , uska khayal hai ke uski qirat Allah ki taraf se hai. Allah ki qasam ! ye (us ki qirat ( to badviyon ke rajz ( chhotey chhotey she'ron ( ki manind hai. Allah ne usey apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par nazil nahin kya hai. aur kon hai jo mujhey un ajmiyon se mazoor janey , un mein se koi pathar phenk deta hai) fitney ki baat kar deta hai) phir kehta hai dekho ye kahan tak jata hai. Allah ki qasam ! main unhen kal maazi ki manind karkey rakh dunga ( neest w nabud kar dunga .) raawi ne kaha ke maine ye waqia Aamash ko bayan kya to usney kaha : maine bhi Allah ki qasam ! usey us se suna hai."
4644,"ibn Idrees ne Aamash se riwayat kya, kaha ke maine Hajjaj se suna wo member par khada keh raha tha : ye ajmi kaat daley janey ke laaiq hain. Allah ki qasam ! maine agar lathi ko lathi par maara to un logon ko maazi ki manind kar chhodunga ( neest w nabud kar dunga .) . uska ishara ghair arab logon ki taraf tha."
4645,"shareek ne Suleman Aamash se riwayat kya, kaha ke maine Hajjaj ke sath Juma padha to usney khutba diya. . . . aur abu-Bakar bin Ayash wali) mazkura baala ( hadees ( 4643 ( bayan ki . usney kaha : Allah ke khalifa aur uskey muntakhab Abdul-Malik bin Marwan ki baat suno aur uski itaat karo . aur hadees bayan ki . mazeed kaha : aur agar main Muzar ke badley Rabeea ki giraft karun. . . . aur ajmiyon ka zikr nahin kya."
4646,"( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghulam ( Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nabuwat ki khilaafat tees saal rahegi phir Allah ta'alaa apna mulk jisey chahega inayat farma dega. Saeed bin Jamhan ne kaha ke Hazrat Safina ne mujhey kaha : hisab laga lo , Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke do saal , Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke das saal , aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke baara saal aur usi tarah kuch Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke . Saeed kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ye Banu-Marwaan samajhtey hain ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa na they to unhoney kaha : bani Zarqa ke pichley hisson ne jhoot bola hai."
4647,"Hazrat Safina (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nabuwat ki khilaafat tees saal tak rahegi . phir Allah taala apna mulk jisey chahega de-dega.''"
4648,"Janab Abdullah bin Zalim Mazni se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke maine Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid bin Amr bin Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhoney kaha : jab falan Kufey mein aaya aur usney falan ko khutbey ke liye khada kya ( Abdullah ne kaha ( to Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne merey haath dabaaey aur kaha : kya tum us zalim ( khateeb ( ko nahin dekhtey ho, ( ghaaliban wo khateeb Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke baarey mein kuch keh raha tha. ( main no afrad ke baarey mein gawahi deta hun ke wo jannati hain, agar daswin ke baarey mein bhi kahun to gunahgaar nahin hunga . . . . ibne-Idrees ne kaha : arab log ( آثم (ka lafz boltey hain ( jabkey Hazrat Saeed ne ( لم إيثم ( .) . . . . Abdullah kehtey hain, maine puchha : wo no afrad kon se hain? unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya jabkey aap Hira par khadey huey they : ''aey Hira thehar ja! tujh par siwaye Nabi ke ya Siddiq ke ya Shaheed ke aur koi nahin hai.'' maine kaha aur wo 9 kon-kon hain? kaha : Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , abu-Bakar , umr , Usman , Ali , Talha , Zuber , Saad bin abi Waqas ( Malik (aur Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) . maine puchha aur daswaan kon hai? to wo lamha bhar ke liye thithkey phir kaha : main . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Ashjai ne Sufiyan sey, unhoney Mansoor sey, unhoney Hilal bin Yusaf sey, unhoney ibne-Hayyan sey, unhoney Abdullah bin Zalim se usi ki sanad se mazkura baala ki manind riwayat kya hai."
4649,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Akhnas se riwayat hai ke wo masjid mein bethey huey they jab eik shakhs ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr kya to Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huey aur kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : '' das log jannati hain. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jannat mein hain, abu-Bakar jannat mein hain, umr jannat mein hain, Usman jannat mein hain, Ali jannat mein hain, Talha jannat mein hain, Zuber bin Awam jannat mein hain, Saad bin Malik jannat mein hain aur Abdur-Rehman bin Auf jannat mein hain.'' agar main chahun to daswen ka naam bhi ley sakta hun. logon ne puchha : wo kon hai? to wo khamosh ho rahey . logon ne puchha : wo kon hai to unhoney kaha : wo Saeed bin Zaid hai."
4650,"Riyah bin Haris ka bayan hai ke main Koofa ki masjid mein falan ke paas betha hua tha. ( ishara hai Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf (aur unke paas ehle koofa ke kuch log bhi bethey huey they. to Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid bin Amr bin Nufail (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif laye . pas unhon ( Mughira ( ne unko marhabaa aur khush aamadeed kaha aur phir unhen apni chaarpai ki paainti ki taraf bitha liya . phir ehle-koofa mein se eik shakhs aaya jis ka naam Qais bin Alqama tha. unhoney uska bhi istaqbal kya. phir usney badgoi ki. Saeed ne puchha ye kisey gaaliyaan dey raha hai? kaha : Hazrat Ali ko . (Raziallahu anhu) . to Saeed ne kaha : ( tajjub hai) mein dekh raha hun ke tumharey samney as-haab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bura bhala kaha ja raha hai aur aap hain ke usey toktey hi nahin aur na samjhaatey hain. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farma rahey they. . . . aur mujhey koi aisi nahin padi ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par koi aisi baat keh dun jo aapney na kahi ho phir kal jab aap se meri mulaqat ho aur wo mujh se poochh lein. . . .'' abu-Bakar jannat mein hai, umr jannat mein hai.'' aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kya. phir kaha : un mein se kisi eik ka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath ( jihad mein) hazir rehna aur uskey chehrey ka ghubar aalud ho jana tumhari sari zindagi ke aamaal se kahin behtar hai chahey tumhen Hazrat Nooh Alehissalam ki zindagi hi kyon na mil jaey."
4651,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Uhud pahad par chadhey to Hazrat abu-Bakar , Hazrat umr aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) bhi aap ke peechey chaley gaey, pas pahad ne harkat ki . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us par apna paon maara aur farmaya : ''Uhud! thehar ja ! ( terey ooper ( eik Nabi , eik Siddiq aur do Shaheed hain."
4652,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey paas Jibrael Alehissalam aaye , mera haath pakda aur mujhey jannat ka wo darwaza dikhlaya jis mein se meri ummat dakhil hogi .'' to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main pasand karta hun kash main bhi aap ke sath hota yahan tak ke usey dekh leta , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum aey abu-Bakar ! yaqinan meri ummat ke wo fard ho jo sab se pehley jannat mein dakhil hogey .''"
4653,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jinhon ne darkht ke nichey baiat ki hai un mein se koi bhi aag mein dakhil nahin hoga .''
4654,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' shayad ke Allah taala ne ehle-Badr par nazar farmaai hai aur kaha hai ke jo chahey amal karo maine tumhen bakhsh diya hai.''
4655,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hudebiya ke dino mein rawana huey . . . . aur hadees bayan ki . . . . kaha ke . . . . phir ( mushrekin ki taraf sey) Urwa bin Masood aaya aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baat kerney laga aur is beech mein wo aap ki dadhi Mubarak ko bhi haath lagata tha. jabkey Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar par khadey huey they, unke haath mein talwaar aur sar par khod thi. to unhoney apni talwaar ke dastey se Urwa ke haath ko tahoka diya aur kaha : aap ki dadhi Mubarak se apna haath door rakh . Urwa ne apna sar ooper uthaya aur puchha : ye kon hai? Sahaba ne kaha : ye Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba hain. (Raziallahu anhu)"
4656,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke muazzan Janab Aqra (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey Esaiyon ke mazhabi sardar ke paas bheja . main usey bula laya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se puchha : kya tum apni kitab mein mera zikr paatey ho? kaha : haan . puchha : kaisey? kaha : main paata hun ke aap eik qarn hain. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna durra us par buland kya aur puchha : ''Qarn'' se kya murad hai? kaha : bahut sakht foladi qila, intehai ameen. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : jo merey baad aaeyga uskey baarey mein kya paatey ho? kaha : wo eik saleh khalifa hoga, sirf itna hoga ke wo apney qurbat daaron ko tarjeeh dega. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) par rehem farmaai , teen baar kaha . phir puchha : unke baad jo aaeyga uskey baarey mein kya paatey ho? kaha : main usey paata hun ke wo lohey ka zang hoga. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna haath apney sar par rakh liya aur kaha : aey badbudar! aey badbudar ! ( kya keh rahey ho? ( to usney kaha : ameerul-momeneen ! ye saleh khalifa hoga magar jab usey ye mansab milega to talwaarein nikli hui hongi aur khoon bahaaey ja rahey hongey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke) الدفر (ke maani hain : '' badbu'' ."
4657,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ka behtareen zamana yehi hai jis mein main mab'oos kya gaya hun, phir wo jo un se muttasil hongey, aur phir wo jo un se muttasil hongey .aur Allah hi jaanta hai ki aapney ye teesri baar farmaya ke nahin. . . . phir unke baad aisey log aaeyngey jo gawahiyan dengey halanke un se gawahi maangi na gaee hogi , nazrein maanengey magar puri nahin karengey . khiyanatein karengey aur un par aitimaad nahin kya jaeyga aur un mein motaapa bhi aam hoga.''"
4658,"Hazrat abu-Saeed ( Khudri ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey Sahaba ki badgoi mat karo. qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar tum mein se koi Uhud pahad jitna sona bhi kharch kar daley to wo unke eik mud ya aadhey ko bhi nahin pahunch sakta.  ( Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hamen utaaridi ne hadees bayan ki, usney kaha : hamen abu-Muaawia ne bayan kya aur hadees bayan ki)"
4659,"Amr bin Abu-Qara ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) madaain mein they aur aisi baaten bayan kar diya kartey they jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baaz Sahaba se narazi ki haalat mein kahi thin. chunanche jin logon ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se ye baaten suni hotin wo Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ko aa kar batatey . to Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey : Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) jo kehtey hain unhen hi unka ziyada pata hoga. log Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aatey aur kehtey ke ham ne aap ki baat Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney zikr ki to unhoney aap ki tasdeeq ki na takzeeb. chunanche Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye jabkey wo mabzi ke eik khet mein they. unhoney kaha : Salman! aap ko kya cheez rukawat hai ke jo baaten maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hain aap un mein meri tasdeeq nahin kartey hain? Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) naraz bhi ho jaya kartey they aur us haalat mein apney Sahaba se kuch keh bhi diya kartey they aur khush bhi hotey they aur us haalat mein bhi apney Sahaba se kuch kehtey they, to kya aap apney us andaz se baaz nahin aa saktey . kya aap logon ke dilon mein kuch ki mohabbat paida karna chahtey hain aur kuch ke mutalliq bughz dal dena chahtey hain? is tarah to aap un logon mein ikhtilaf w iftiraaq paida kar dengey , halanke main b-khoobi janta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik khutba diya aur farmaya tha : '' (aey Allah ! ( apni ummat ke jis kisi ko maine kabhi koi bura bhala kaha ho ya narazi ki haalat mein lanat ki ho to main bhi Adam zaad hun, jis tarah wo ghussey mein aa jatey hain main bhi aa jata hun aur mujhey jahan walon ke liye rehmat bana kar bheja hai) ya Allah ! meri in baaton ko) unke liye qiyamat ke roz rehmat bana dey.'' (aey Huzefa ! ( Allah ki qasam ! tum baaz aa jao ya mein umr ko likh bhejunga . phir kuch logon ne un se sifarish ki to unhoney apni qasam ka kaffara ada kar diya aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko na likha. aur kaffara bhi qasam todney se pehley diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : qasam ka kaffara, qasam todney se pehley ada karna ya baad mein ada karna sab jayez hai."
4660,"Janab Abdullah bin Zam-aa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki takleef bahut badh gaee aur main musalmanon ki eik jamaat ke sath aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ko Namaz ke liye bulaya . aapney farmaya : '' kisi se keh do , wo logon ko Namaz padha dey .'' Abdullah bin Zam-aa kehtey hain ke main nikla to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) mojud they jabke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mojud nahin they. maine kaha : aey umr ! uthiye aur logon ko Namaz padha diijiye . chunanche wo aagey badhey aur takbir kahi .) udhar ( jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki aawaz suni . . . . aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) buland aawaz aadmi they. . . . to farmaya : '' abu-Bakar kahan hain? Allah uska inkar karta hai aur musalman bhi . Allah uska inkar karta hai aur musalman bhi .'' pas aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja to wo aagey jabkey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko Namaz padha chukey they, phir Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon ko wohi Namaz padhaai ."
4661,"Janab Abdullah bin Zam-aa (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye khabar bayan ki ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aawaz suni to aap tashrif laye, apna sar Mubarak hujrey se nikala aur farmaya : '' nahin. nahin . nahin. ibne-abi qahaafa ( abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) logon ko Namaz padhaein .'' aapney ye baat narazi ki keyfiyat mein farmaai."
4662,"Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Saiyedna Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke mutalliq farmaya : '' mera ye beta sardar hai aur mujhey umeed hai ke Allah taala iskey zariey se meri ummat ke do girohon mein suleh kara dega.'' Hammad ki riwayat ke alfaz hain : ''aur umeed hai ke Allah taala uskey zariey se musalmanon ke do badey girohon mein suleh kara dega.''"
4663,"Janab Muhammad bin Sirin (Rahimahullah) ne riwayat kya ke Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke logon mein koi aisa nahin ke usey koi fitna darpesh ho (aur wo us se mehfooz rahey) mujhey andesha rehta hai ke wo us mein mubtala ho jaeyga, siwaye Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ke, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap (unhen) farma rahey they : '' tujhey fitna nuqsan nahin dega .''"
4664,"Janab Solba bin Zabeeaa kehtey hain ke ham Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey to unhoney kaha : main yaqinan is aadmi ko janta hun jisey fitney koi nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakengey. kaha ke phir ham unke yahan se nikley to hamen eik khema nazar aaya, ham us mein chaley gaey, to dekha ke us mein Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) hain. ham ne un se us (tanhai aur gosha geeri) ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : main nahin chahta ke tumharey shehron ka koi fitna mujhey apni lapet mein le-ley yahan tak ke ye soorate-haal saaf ho jaey. ( fitney khatam ho jaeyn .)"
4665,abu-Barda ne bayan kya ke Zabeeaa bin Husain Solbi ne mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kya.
4666,"Janab Qais bin Ibaad kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap ka (Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke muqabley mein) nikalna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ki bina par hai ya ye aapki apni zaati raey hai? unhoney kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuch nahin farmaya tha, balke ye meri apni zaati raey hai."
4667,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalmanon mein iftiraaq ke waqt eik fitna angez jamaat niklegi jisey musalmanon ka wo garoh qatl kerega jo haq ke ziyada qarib hoga.''"
4668,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' anbiya ko eik doosrey par fazilat w tarjeeh mat diya karo.''"
4669,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kisi bandey ko laaiq nahin ke wo yun kahey ke main ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( Hazrat Yunus bin Matti Alehissalam se behtar hun.''"
4670,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : '' kisi Nabi ko laaiq nahin ke yun kahey ke main Hazrat Yunus bin Matti Alehissalam se behtar hun.''"
4671,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik yahudi ne kaha : qasam us zaat ki jisney Musa Alehissalam ko muntakhab farmaya , to eik musalman ne apna haath uthaya aur yahudi ke munh par thappad maar diya. wo yahudi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chala aaya aur aap ko bataya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey Musa Alehissalam par fazilat mat do . bila-shuba ( qiyamat barpa honey par) jab log be hosh kiye jaeyngey to main hi hunga jo sab se pehley hosh mein aaunga aur dekhunga ke Musa Alehissalam arsh ka paya pakdey khadey hongey. maloom nahin wo be-hosh huey hongey aur mujh se pehley hosh mein aagey hongey ya ye un afrad mein se hon jinhen Allah taala ne be-hoshi se mustashnaa rakha hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ibn Yahya ki riwayat ziyada mukammal hai."
4672,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yun khitab kya ( يا خير البرية ) ''aey makhluq mein sab se afzal shakhsiyat ! '' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Hazrat Ibrahim Alehissalam they.''
4673,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main aulad Adam ka sardar hun aur pehla shakhs hunga jis se zameen phategi, main sab se pehley sifarish karunga aur meri sifarish hi sab se pehley qubul hogi.''"
4674,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( tubba (ke mutalliq mujhey nahin maloom wo laeen (laanti) tha ya nahin. aur uzair ke mutalliq khabar nahin ke wo Nabi tha ya nahin .''"
4675,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''main ibne-Maryam Alehissalam ke sab se ziyada qarib hon aur anbiya goya eik baap ki aulad hain (jinki maaeyn alag alag hon) merey aur ibne-Maryam ke darmiyan aur koi Nabi nahin .''"
4676,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''emaan ki sattar aur kuch shaakhen hain. sab se afzal ( '' La-ilaah-illallah '' ( kehna hai aur sab se nichey ye hai ke koi raastey mein padi haddi door kar dey . aur haya bhi emaan ki eik shaakh hai.''"
4677,"abu-Jamra se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se suna, unhoney farmaya : jab abdul-Qais ka wafad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya to aapney unhen Allah par emaan laney ka hukm diya. aapney un se puchha : ''kya jantey ho Allah par emaan lana kya hai? '' unhoney kaha : Allah aur uska Rasool hi behtar jantey hain. aapney farmaya : '' sirf eik Allah ke mabud haqeeqi honey aur Muhammad ke Rasulullah honey ki gawahi dena , Namaz qaaim karna , Zakat dena , Ramazan ke rozey rakhna aur ye ke tum maal ghanimat mein se paanchwan hissey ada karo.''"
4678,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bandey aur kufr ke darmiyan farq Namaz chhod dena hai.''"
4679,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( aurton ko khitab kartey huey ( farmaya : ''maine kisi naqis aql aur naqis deen wali ko nahin paya jo tum se badh kar aqlmand bandey ko be aql bana deney wali ho.'' eik aurat boli : aql aur deen mein kami aur nuqs kaisey hai? aapney farmaya : '' aql ki kami ye hai ke do aurton ki gawahi eik mard ke barabar hoti hai aur deen mein kami yun hai ke bila-shuba aurat Ramazan ke doran mein rozey chhod deti hai aur kaee kaee din Namaz nahin padhti .''
4680,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke) tahweel qibla ke moqe par) jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaaba ki taraf rukh kar liya to Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! un logon ka kya hoga jo baitul-Maqdis ki taraf munh karkey namazein padhtey rahey, tu Allah taala ne ye aayat nazil farmaai: وما كان الله ليضيع إيمانكم  ''Allah taala aisa nahin hai ke tumharey eimaanon ko zaya kar dey .''"
4681,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney Allah ki khatir mohabbat ki, Allah ki khatir ghussa kya, Allah ke liye diya, aur Allah ki razamandi ke peshe-nazar na diya to usney emaan ko kamil kar liya.''"
4682,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ahle-eman mein sab se badh kar kamil emaan wala wohi hai jo akhlaq mein sab se badh kar ho.''"
4683,"Janab Aamir bin Saad apney walid ( Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke) eik baar ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baaz logon ko kuch inayat farmaya aur eik aadmi ko kuch na diya. to Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney falan falan ko inayat farmaya hai aur falan ko kuch nahin diya halanke wo momin hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ya Muslim hai.'' Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye baat teen baar kahi aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ya Muslim hai, Muslim hai farmatey rahey aur phir kaha : ''main baaz aadmiyon ko deta hun aur baaz ko chhod deta hun halanke wo mujhey unki nisbat ziyada mehboob hotey hain is andeshey se ke kahin wo apney munhon ke bal aag mein na dal diye jaeyn.''"
4684,Janab ibne-Shahab Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne aayate-karima ( قل لم تؤمنوا ولكن قولوا أسلمنا ( '' keh diijiye ! (aey badviyon ! ( tum emaan nahin laye balke yun kaho ke ham ne Islam qubul kya hai.'' ki tafseer mein bayan kya ke ham samajhtey hain Islam se murad zabani iqrar hai aur emaan se murad amal hai.
4685,"Janab Aamir apney walid Hazrat Saad (bin abi Waqas ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne musalmanon mein kuch maal taqseem kya to maine arz kya : falan ko bhi diijiye bila-shuba wo momin hai. aapney farmaya : '' ya Muslim hai, beshak mein kisi shakhs ko koi Atiya deta hun halanke uskey bajaey koi doosra mujhey ziyada mehboob hota hai, ( usey kuch nahin deta ( mein is andeshey se usey deta hun ke kahin ondhey munh na gira diya jaey.''"
4686,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kahen merey baad kafir na bin jana ke eik doosrey ki gardanen maarney lago .''"
4687,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kisi musalman ne kisi musalman ko kafir kaha, to agar wo (haqeeqat mein) kafir hua to (bahut theek) , warna kehney wala hi kafir hai.''"
4688,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' chaar khaslatein jis shakhs mein pai jaeyn wo khalis munafiq hota hai aur jis mein un mein se koi eik ho to us mein nifaq ki eik khaslat hoti hai yahan tak ke wo usey chhod dey . yani jab baat karey to jhoot boley , wada karey to khilaf karey, ehad muahida karey to dhoka dey aur agar jhagda ho jaey to bad-zabaani ( gaali galoch) par utar aaye .''"
4689,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bad-kar zaani jis waqt zina kar raha ho, iimaandar nahin hota . chor jis waqt chori kar raha ho, emaan wala nahin hota, aur shraabi jab sharab pi raha ho, momin nahin hota, uskey baad tauba uskey samney hai.''"
4690,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi jab zina karta hai to emaan us se nikal jata hai aur uskey ooper chhatri ki manind ho jata hai. pas jab wo apni bad-kari se nikal aata hai to emaan uski taraf wapis aa jata hai.''"
4691,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Qadriya ( taqdir ka inkar kerney waley ( is ummat ke majusi hain. agar bimar ho jaeyn to unki iyaadat ko mat jao aur agar mar jaeyn to janaazey mein shareek na ho.''"
4692,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her ummat ke majusi hotey hain aur is ummat ke majusi wo hain jo taqdir ke munkir hain. un mein se jo mar jaey uskey janaazey mein mat jao aur jo bimar ho uski iyaadat ke liye mat jao . yehi log dajjaal ke haami hongey aur Allah par haq hai ke unhen dajjaal ke sath milaaey .''"
4693,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall ne Adam ko eik mutthi mitti se paida kya hai jisey usney tamam ruey zameen se jama farmaya tha. chunanche Adam ki aulad is mitti ke lihaz se hui hai, kaee surkh hain aur kaee safed, kaee siyah hain aur kaee unke darmyan. kaee naram khoo hain aur kaee sakht tabiat . kaee buri tabiat ke Malik hotey hain aur kaee achi aur umda tabiat waley .'' Yahya bin Saeed ki riwayat mein izafa hai : '' aur kaee unke darmiyan hain.'' Yazid (bin zareea' ( ki riwayat mein) أخبرنا (ka seegha istimal hua hai."
4694,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham baqee gharqad ke qabristaan main eik janaazey mein they jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi they. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur beth gaey, aap ke haath mein khoonti thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) us se zameen kuredney lagey . phir aapney apna sar uthaya aur farmaya : ''Allah taala ne tum mein se her her jaan ka maqam jahannam ya jannat mein likh diya hai aur uskey baarey mein likha ja chuka hai ke wo bad-bakht hai ya sa'adat mand .'' to qom mein se eik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! to kya phir ham apney us likhey huey par na ruk jaeyn aur amal chhod den . jo ehle-sa'adat mein se hoga apni sa'adat ko pa lega aur jo bad-bakht hoga apni bad-bakhti ko pa lega . aapney farmaya : '' amal kiye jao . her eik tofiq diya gaya hai. nek bakhton ko sa'adat ke aamaal ki tofiq di jati hai aur bad-bakhton ko bad-bakhton waley aamaal ki tofiq milti hai.'' phir Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayaat padhein : ( { فَأَمَّا مَنْ أَعْطَى . . . . فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْعُسْرَى } (aur jisney ( Allah ke liye maal ( diya aur taqwa ikhtiyar kya aur neki ki tasdeeq ki, ham usey aasan manzil ki tofiq detey hain. aur jisney bukhl kya aur beparwa bana raha aur neki ko jhutlaya , to ham usey tangi wali manzil ki tofiq detey hain.''"
4695,"Yahya bin Yamar (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke) musalmanon mein) sab se pehley jisney taqdir ka inkar kya wo Basrey ka Maabad Johni tha. chunanche main aur Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman Himyari hajj ya Umerey ke liye rawana huey to ham ne kaha : kash Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se kisi se hamari mulaqat ho jaey jis se ham un logon ke baarey mein poochh saken jo taqdir mein kalam kartey hain. ( inkar kartey hain. ( tu Allah ka karna aisey hua ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) hamen masjid mein dakhil hotey huey mil gaey . chunanche merey sathi aur maine unko apney pahluon mein ley liya aur mujhey khayal hua ke mera sathi mujhey baat kerney dega . chunanche maine kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! ( Abdullah bin umr ! ( hamarey ird-gird kuch aisey log namudaar huey hain jo Quran padh kar ilm ki baareekiyaan nikaltey hain. unka khayal hai ke taqdir kuch nahin hai aur maamlat wesay hi ho jatey hain. to unhoney kaha : tum jab un se milo to unhen bata dena ke main ( Abdullah bin umr (us zaat aali ki jiski Abdullah bin umr qasam uthaya karta hai ! ( Allah taala ki ! ( un mein se koi agar Uhud pahad jitna sona bhi kharch kar daley tu Allah usey qubul nahin kerega jab tak wo taqdir par emaan na ley aaye. phir kaha : mujh se Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bethey huey they ke achcha eik aadmi aa gaya jiskey kapdey intehai safed aur baal nihayat kalay they, us par safar ke koi aasaar dikhai na detey they aur ham mein se koi usey pahchaanta bhi na tha. wo aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney beth gaya. usney apney ghutney aap ke ghutnon ke sath mila liye aur apni hatheliyan bhi aap ki raanon par rakh den aur kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! mujhey Islam ke mutalliq batlaaiye ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Islam ye hai ke tum gawahi do ke eik Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin aur Muhammad Allah ke Rasool hain. Namaz qaaim karo, Zakat ada karo, Ramazan ke rozey rakho aur Baitullah ka hajj karo agar us tak pahunchney ki istataat ho.'' kehney laga : aapney sach farmaya. hamen is par bahut tajjub hua ke aap se sawal bhi karta hai aur tasdeeq bhi karta hai. phir kehney laga : aap mujhey emaan ke mutalliq batlaayein? aapney farmaya : ''(emaan ye hai) ke tum Allah par, uskey farishton, uski kitabon, uskey Rasulon aur aakhirat ke din par emaan lao aur taqdir ke achey aur burey honey par bhi emaan lao.'' usney kaha : aapney sach farmaya. phir bola mujhey ehsan ke mutalliq batlaayein? aapney farmaya : ''Allah ki ibadat is tarah se karo goya ke tum usey dekh rahey ho, agar ye keyfiyat hasil na ho to ye ho ke wo tumhen dekh raha hai.'' usney kaha ke mujhey qiyamat ke mutalliq batlaayein ? aapney farmaya : '' uski baabat jis se poochh rahey ho, wo poochhney waley se ziyada nahin janta .'' tab usney kaha : achcha mujhey uski alaamaat bata den ? aapney farmaya : ''ye ke londi apni maalika ko janam dey aur tum dekho ke paon aur jism se nangey , faqir aur bakriyon ke charwahey oonchi oonchi imaraten bananey main eik doosrey se badhney lag jaeyn .'' phir wo chala gaya. phir main ( umr bin Khattab ( teen din rukaa raha to aapney farmaya : ''aey umr ! kya tumhen khabar hai wo saail kon tha ?'' maine arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool hi behtar jantey hain. aapney farmaya : '' beshak wo Jibrael tha jo tumhen tumhara deen sikhaaney aaya tha.''"
4696,"Janab Yahya bin Yaamar aur Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne bayan kya ke ham Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se miley aur un se taqdir aur deegar masayel jo wo log boltey they, daryaft kiye. . . . to mazkura baala hadees ki manind zikr kiye aur mazeed kaha : muzena ya juhaina ke aadmi ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham amal kis bina par keren? kya ye jaan kar ke sab kuch tey ho chuka hai ya ye samajh kar ke maamla naya hai? aapney farmaya : ''ye samajh kar ke sab kuch tey ho chuka hai.'' to qom mein se eik ne kaha : to phir amal kyon hain? aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba jannati ehle-jannat ke amalon ki tofiq diye jatey hain aur dozakhi ehle-jahannam ke amalon ki tofiq diye jatey hain.''"
4697,"Janab Suleman bin Barida ne ibn Yaamar se ye riwayat naqal ki jis mein kuch kami beshi hai) uskey alfaz mein .) kaha : Islam kya hai? farmaya : '' Namaz qaaim karna , Zakat dena , Baitullah ka hajj karna , maahe-Ramazan ke rozey rakhna aur janabat se ghusl karna . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Alqama (bin Marsad) ka talluq firqa marjiya se tha."
4698,"Hazrat abu-Zar aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney Sahaba ke darmiyan betha kartey they. chunanche jab koi naya aanewala aata to wo aap ko pehchan na paata tha yahan tak ke aap ke mutalliq poochhtey (ke Rasulullah kon hain? ( to ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya ke aap ke liye khas jagah bana den taake wo naya aanewala jab aaye to aap ko pehchan liya karey. chunanche ham ne aap ke liye mitti ka eik chabootra sa bana diya aur aap us par bethney lagey aur ham uskey atraaf mein beth jaya kartey they. aur mazkura baala khabar (hadees) ki manind bayan kya. chunanche eik aadmi aaya aur uski shakal w soorat bayan ki, yahan tak ke usney jamaat ki eik janib se salam kya aur kaha : Assalaamu alaik ya Muhammad! Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey salam ka jawab diya."
4699,"Janab ( Abdullah bin feeroz ( Ibne-Delmi ne kaha : main Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur arz kya ke merey dil mein taqdir ke baarey mein kuch shubha sa hai. mujhey koi hadees bayan kijiye taake Allah taala merey dil se ye waswasa door kar dey . chunanche unhoney kaha : agar Allah taala apney tamam aasman walon aur apney tamam zameen walon ko azab dena chahey to wo un par zalim nahin hoga aur agar wo un par rehmat karey to unki rehmat unke liye unke aamaal se bahut behtar hai. aur agar tum Uhud pahad jitna sona bhi Allah taala ki raah mein kharch kar dalo to jab tak taqdir par emaan nahin laogey Allah taala usey tum se qubul nahin kerega aur) jab tak ( ye na jaan lo ke jo kuch tumhen pahuncha hai, wo kisi soorat faut nahin ho sakta tha aur jo hasil nahin hua , wo kisi soorat hasil nahin ho sakta tha. agar tum us aqidey ke siwa kisi aur par mar gaey to jahannam mein jaogey .) Ibne-Delmi ( kehtey hain ke phir main Hazrat Abdullah Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya to unhoney bhi aisey hi kaha . unhoney kaha : phir main Hazrat Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya , to unhoney bhi aisey hi kaha . phir main Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya , to unhoney bhi mujh se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se usi ki misl bayan kya."
4700,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ne apney bete se kaha : merey bete ! to us waqt tak emaan ki haqeeqat nahin pa sakta jab tak ye yaqeen na kar ley ke jo kuch tumhen hasil ho chuka hai, ye tum se reh nahin sakta tha aur jo hasil nahin hua hai, wo mil nahin sakta tha. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : '' sab se pehli chiz jo Allah ne paida farmaai wo qalam thi. phir us se farmaya ke likho , usney kaha : aey merey rab ! kya likhun ? Allah taala ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim honey tak her her chiz ki taqdir likh .'' aey merey bete ! beshak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai aap farmatey they : ''jo shakhs uskey siwa ( kisi aur aqidey ( par mar gaya wo mujh se nahin .''"
4701,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kiya. aapney bayan farmaya : '' Hazrat Adam aur Hazrat Musa (Alaihimussalaam) mein behes ho gaee . Musa Alehissalam ne kaha : aey Adam ! aap hamarey walid hain, aapney hamen bahut ghaata diya aur jannat se nikal diya. Adam ne kaha : tum Musa ho, Allah ne tumhen apney sath ham kalam honey ka sharf bakhsha aur tumharey liye apney haath se Taurath likhi . tum mujhey eik aisi baat (taqdir) par malamat kar rahey ho jo usney merey paida honey se chaalis saal pehley hi merey liye muqaddar kar di thi. chunanche Adam Alehissalam Musa Alehissalam par ghalib aagey . Ahmed bin Saleh ne sanad yun bayan ki . . . .) (an) Amr (an) Taaoos, Samia' Abu Huraira (Raziallahu anhu)) ."
4702,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Hazrat Musa Alehissalam ne dua ki : aey merey Rab ! hamen Adam Alehissalam dikhla , jinhon ne hamen aur apney aap ko bhi jannat se nikal diya tha. chunanche Allah taala ne unko Adam Alehissalam dikhla diye , to Hazrat Musa Alehissalam ne kaha : aap hamarey baap Adam hain? Adam Alehissalam ne Musa Alehissalam se kaha : haan . Musa Alehissalam ne kaha : aap hi wo hain jis mein Allah ne apni rooh phunki thi aur tamam chizon ke naam taaleem farmaai they aur tamam farishton ko hukm diya tha to unhoney aap ko sajda kiya tha? kaha : haan . Musa Alehissalam ne kaha : aap ko kis chiz ne aamada kiya ke aapney hamen aur apney aap ko jannat se nikal bahir kiya? Adam Alehissalam ne un se kaha : aur tum kon ho? unhoney kaha : main Musa hun. kaha tum hi Bani-Israel ke wo Nabi ho jis se Allah taala ne pardey ke peechhey se kalam farmaya tha aur apney aur tumharey darmiyan apni makhluq mein se kisi ko wasta nahin banaya tha? kaha : haan . Adam Alehissalam ne kaha : kya tum ne nahin paya ke ye sab kuchh merey paida kiye janey se pehley hi Kitabe Allah main (aisey hi) tha? Musa Alehissalam ne kaha : haan . Adam Alehissalam ne kaha : to phir tum mujhey kis chiz par malamat kartey ho, halanke wo mujh se pehley hi Allah ke faisley mein thi.'' us par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Adam Alehissalam Musa Alehissalam par daleel mein ghalib aagey.''"
4703,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se ( وإذ أخذ ربك من بني آدم من ظهورهم . . ) الخ ''aur jab terey Rab ne bano Adam ki peethon se unki aulad nikali aur unhen khud unhi par gawah thehraya , kya main tumhara Rab nahin hun? unhoney kaha : haan , ham iqrar kartey hain.'' ki tafseer poochhi gaee to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap se uskey baarey mein puchha gaya tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shan Wale Allah ne Adam Alehissalam ko paida kiya, phir apna dahina haath uski pusht par phera aur us se uski aulad nikali aur farmaya : inko maine jannat ke liye paida kiya hai aur ye jannatiyon waley amal karengey. phir uski pusht par haath phera aur us se uski aulad nikali aur farmaya : inko maine dozakh ke liye paida kiya hai aur ye dozakhiyon waley amal karengey.'' eik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! to phir amal kyonkar hain? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Shan Wale Allah ne jab bandey ko jannat ke liye paida kiya hai to us se ehle jannat waley amal karwaana hai yahan tak ke wo ehle jannat ke amal karta hua mar jaeyga tu Allah unhi aamaal ki wajeh se usey jannat mein dakhil farma dega aur jab kisi bandey ko aag ke liye paida kiya hai to us se dozakhiyon waley amal karwaana hai yahan tak ke wo dozakhiyon waley amal karta hua mar jaeyga tu Allah usi ke sabab se usey aag mein dal dega.''"
4704,Janab Naeem bin Rabeea kehtey hain ke main Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha. . . . aur hadees riwayat ki . aur (mazkura baala) hadees Maalik ziyada mukammal hai.
4705,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo ladka jisey khizr ne qatl kiya tha wo kafir paida kiya gaya tha. agar zinda rehta to apney maa baap ko sarkashi aur kufr par majboor kar deta.''"
4706,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : aap Allah taala ke farman (وأما الغلام فكان أبواه مؤمنين) ''aur us ladkey ke maa baap momin they.'' ki tafseer mein farma rahey they : '' wo ladka jis din paida kiya gaya, kafir paida kiya gaya tha.''"
4707,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Hazrat khizr Alehissalaam ne ladkey ko dekha jo doosrey bachon ke sath khel raha tha. to unhoney uska sar pakad kar marod diya. to Musa Alehissalaam boley : ''aapney eik paak jaan ko qatl kar dala hai.''"
4708,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ham se bayan farmaya , aur aap saadiq aur masdooq hain. ( Allah taala ki taraf se aur uskey malaaika , anbiya aur rasool aur momineen ki janib se aap ki tasdeeq ki gaee hai) ''tumhari paidaish ke marhale mein nutfa maa ke pet mein chaalis din tak rehta hai, phir itney hi din jama hua khoon (loathra) bin jata hai. phir itney hi dino ke liye gosht ki boti bin jata hai. phir Allah taala uski taraf eik farishta bhejta hai aur usey chaar baaten likhney ka hukm hota hai. wo uska rizq , ajal (Umar ya maut) , amal aur ye ke wo khush bakht hoga ya bad-bakht , ye sab likh deta hai. phir us mein rooh phunk di jati hai. chunanche yaqinan tum mein se koi ehle jannat waley amal karta hai yahan tak ke uskey aur us ( jannat (ke darmiyan sirf eik haath ka fasla reh jata hai, magar us se pehley jis tarah likha hua hai uskey mutabiq dozakhiyon waley amal shuru kar deta hai aur dozakh mein ja padta hai. aur beshak tum mein se koi dozakhiyon waley amal karta rehta hai yahan tak ke uskey aur dozakh ke darmiyan sirf eik haath ka fasla reh jata hai, lekin us se pehley jo likha hai uskey mutabiq wo jannatiyon wala amal kar leta hai aur jannat mein chala jata hai.''"
4709,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya dozakhiyon ke muqabley mein jannatiyon ko jana ja chuka hai? aapney farmaya : ''haan'' kaha gaya : to phir amal kerney waley kyonkar amal kartey hain? aapney farmaya : ''her eik ko usi ki taufiq milti hai jis ke liye usey paida kiya gaya hai.''"
4710,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''munkereene-taqdir ke sath mat baitha karo aur na un se baat cheet (ya munaazrey) ki ibtida (shuruat) kiya karo.''"
4711,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mushrekin ki aulad ke mutalliq puchha gaya ( jo bachpan mein faut ho jatey hain ( to aapney farmaya : ''Allah ko khoob ilm hai ke wo ( badey ho kar) kya amal karney waley they.''
4712,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mominon ki auladon ka kya anjam hoga? to aapney farmaya : ''wo apney aabaa (baap-daada) mein se hain.'' maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! amal ke baghair hi ? farmaya : ''Allah ko khoob ilm hai ke wo kya amal karney waley they.'' maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mushrikon ki auladon ka anjam kya hoga? aapney farmaya : ''wo apney aabaa mein se hain, maine kaha : amal ke baghair hi ? farmaya : ''Allah ko behtar ilm hai jo wo amal karney waley they.''"
4713,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya, unhoney kaha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas Ansariyon ka eik bachha laya gaya ke aap uski Namaze janaza padhaeyn. kehti hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Mubarak ho usey ! usney koi bura amal nahin kiya, na burey amalon ki usey koi khabar hi hui . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aaisha ! ya phir is se mukhtalif? beshak Shan Wale Allah ne jannat paida farmaai to uskey liye makhluq bhi paida kar di aur us jannat ko unhi ke liye banaya jabkey wo abhi apney baapon ki pushton mein hotey hain. aur aag ( jahannam ( paida ki to uskey liye makhluq bhi paida kar di aur us jahannam ko un hi logon ke liye banaya jabkey wo abhi apney baapon ki pushton mein hotey hain.''"
4714,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''her paida honey wala bachcha fitrat par paida hota hai (deene-haq , Islam aur toheed ka hamil hota hai). phir uskey maa baap usey yahudi aur esai bana detey hain, jaisey oont ka bacha sahih Salim janm leta hai, kya tum kisi ko kaan kataa paatey ho ?'' logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! uskey mutalliq farmaeyn jo chhoti umr mein faut ho jata hai? farmaya : ''Allah ko behtar ilm hai jo wo amal kartey.''"
4715,"Imam Maalik (Rahimahullah) se kaha gaya ke ehle ahwaa , yani bid'ati log ye mazkura hadees hamarey khilaf pesh kartey hain (inkar taqdir aur asbaat jabr mein). Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : tum usi hadees ke aakhiri hissey ko un par ulta diya karo .) jis mein hai ke) logon ne kaha : us bachchey ke mutalliq farmaeyn jo chhoti umr mein faut ho jata hai? aapney farmaya : ''Allah ko behtar ilm hai jo wo amal kartey .''"
4716,"Janab Hammad bin Salma ne hadees : ''har bachcha fitrat par paida hota hai.'' ki tashreeh mein kaha : ''uska mafhoom hamarey nazdik ye hai ke ye us waqt ki baat hai jab Shan Wale Allah ne roohon se ehad liya jabkey wo apney baapon ki pushton mein they, us waqt kaha tha ( ألست بربكم ( ''kya main tumhara rab nahin hun ?'' to sab ne kaha : kyon nahin."
4717,"Janab Aamir Shobi (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bachchey ko zinda dafn karney wali aur zinda dafn honey wali) dono ( aag mein hain. Yahya bin Zakariya ne kaha : merey walid ne kaha ke mujhey Abu-Is'haq ne bayan kiya ke Aamir ne usko ye hadees b-waaste Alqama, Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan ki thi."
4718,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mera baap kahan hai? aapney farmaya : ''tera baap aag mein hai.'' jab usney gardan pheri to aapney farmaya : ''mera baap aur tera baap jahannam mein hain.''
4719,"Hazrat Anas bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba shaitan ibne-Adam ke jism mein is tarah gardish karta hai jaisey khoon.''"
4720,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''munkareene-taqdir ki sohbat se bacho aur un se baat cheet (aur munaazrey ( mein ibtida (shuruat) na kiya karo.''"
4721,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''log sawalat kartey rahengey yahan tak ke kaha jaeyga : ye makhluq Allah ne paida ki hai tu Allah ko kis ne paida kiya? so jo koi is qism ki baat karey (ya weham paey ( to usey chahiye ke yun kahey : ''main Allah par emaan laya.''"
4722,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna, kehtey they. . . . aur mazkura baala ki manind bayan kiya. kaha : ''jab wo log ye kahen to tum kaho : Allah eik hai. Allah be-niyaz hai. na usney jana aur na wo jana gaya aur koi nahin jo uski barabari kar sakey . phir chahiye ke baain janib kuchh luaab thookey aur shaitan ke shar se Allah ki panah maangey.''"
4723,"Saiyedna Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kehtey hain : main wadi Bat'haa main eik jamaat mein baitha hua tha jis mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi tashrif farma they, wahan se badal ka eik tukda guzra . aapney uski taraf dekha aur puchha : ''tum log isey kya kehtey ho ?'' unhoney kaha : (سحاب) aapney farmaya : '' aur (مزن) bhi?'' unhoney kaha : haan (مزن) bhi . aapney farmaya : '' aur (عنان) bhi?'' unhoney kaha : haan (عنان) bhi kehtey hain. . . . . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : mujhey ( العنان (ka zikr koi ziyada achchhi tarah yaad nahin hai. . . aapney farmaya : ''kya jantey ho aasman aur zameen mein kitna fasla hai?'' unhoney kaha : hamein maloom nahin. aapney farmaya : ''in dono ke darmiyan ikhattar ya bahttar ya tehattar saal ka fasla hai. phir uskey baad doosrey aasman ka bhi itna hi fasla hai.'' yahan tak ke aapney saat aasman shumar kiye. phir farmaya : ''saatwen ke ooper samandar hai jiski gehraai aur oonchaai is qadr hai jaisey eik aasman se doosrey aasman tak , phir uskey ooper aath bakrey hain jinkey khuron aur ghutnon ke darmiyan is qadr fasla hai jaisey eik aasman se doosrey aasman tak , phir unki pushton par arsh hai, jiski tahiya aur oonchaai mein itna hi fasla hai jaisey eik aasman se doosrey aasman tak . phir us se ooper Allah tabarak w taala hai.''"
4724,Janab Amr bin Abu-Qais ne ba-waaste Simaak apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya.
4725,Janab Ibrahim bin Tahmaan ne ba-waaste Simaak iski sanad se mazkura baala taweel hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya.
4726,"Janab Jubair bin Muhammad bin Jubair bin Mut-im apney walid Muhammad se wo dada Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik Erab (dehaati) aaya . usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jaanon pe bin aai hai, baal bachchey halak ho rahey hain, maal khatam ho gaey hain, aur maweshi mar rahey hain, Allah se hamarey liye barish talab keejiye . ham Allah ke huzur aap ki sifarish pesh kartey hain aur Allah ko aap ke huzur sifarishi latey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''afsos tujh par ! kya jantey ho ke tum kya keh rahey ho?'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) musalsal tasbih ( Subhanallah ( kehtey rahey yahan tak ke us ( khof ke asar ( ko aap ke Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ke chehron mein mehsoos kiya gaya. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''afsos tujh par ! Allah taala ko uski makhluq mein se kisi ke yahan sifarishi pesh nahin kiya ja sakta. Allah taala ki shaan us se kahin ziyada ba-azmat (aur bartar) hai. afsos tujh par ! kya tum jantey ho ke Allah ki kya shaan hai? bila-shuba uska arsh aasmano par is tarah hai.'' aur aapney apni ungliyon se qubey ki si shakal banai. aur farmaya : ''wo arsh is tarah se char-charaa raha hai jaisey paalaan apney sawar ke sath charcharaataa hai.'' Ibne-Bashar ne apni riwayat mein kaha : ''bila-shuba Allah taala apney arsh se ooper hai. aur uska arsh uskey aasmano se ooper hai.'' . . . . ba-waaste Yaqoob bin Utba aur Jubair bin Muhammad bin Jubair , usney apney walid se usney apney dada se riwayat ki. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aur hadees Ahmed bin Saeed ki sanad se hi sahih hai. aur jamaate-muhaddeseen ne uski muwaafiqat ki hai jin mein Yahya bin Ma'eeni aur Ali bin Madeeni bhi hain. aur eik jamaat ne ibne-Is'haq se usi tarah riwayat kya hai jaisey Ahmed ne kaha aur jaisey ke mujhey riwayat pahunchi hai Abdul-A'alaa , ibne Musanna aur ibne Bashaar ka samaa, (suna) eik hi nuskhey se hai."
4727,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) riwayat kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey kaha gaya hai ke main tumhen haameleen arsh mein se eik farishtey ke mutalliq bataun . bila-shuba uskey kanon ki lau se uskey kandhey tak ka fasla saat sau saal ke safar ke barabar hai.''"
4728,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye aayat kareema padhi : (إن الله يأمركم أن تؤدوا الأمانات إلى أهلها . . سميعا بصيرا) ''bila-shuba Allah tumhen hukm deta hai ke amanaten unke haqdaaron ko pahuncha do aur jab logon ke darmiyan faisla karo to adl aur insaaf ke sath faisla karo, Allah achchhi nasihat karta hai, bila-shuba Allah khoob sunney wala khoob dekhney wala hai.'' kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apna angoothaa apney kaan par aur sath wali ungli apni aankh par rakh rahey they. Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap is aayat ko padhtey huey apni ungliyan ( kaan aur aankh par) rakh rahey they. ibne Yunus ne riwayat kiya ke Abdullah bin Yazid muqri ne kaha : maqsad ye hai ke bila-shuba Allah taala samie' aur baseer hai yani wo khoob sunta aur khoob dekhta hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ismein jahmiya ki tardeed hai (Shan Wala Allah in sifaat wala hai yaqeenan.)"
4729,"Hazrat Jarir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath baithey huey they ke aapney chaand ki taraf nazar uthai jabkey raat chaudahwin ki thi aur chaand khoob chamak raha tha. aapney farmaya : ''tum apney Rab ko dekhogey jaisey isko dekh rahey ho, uskey dekhney mein koi jamghataa nahin hoga , chunanche agar kar saktey ho to ye karo ke Suraj nikalney aur ghuroob honey se pehley ki namazon mein maghloob (peechhey) na ho jao, phir aapney ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ({وَسَبِّحْ بِحَمْدِ رَبِّكَ قَبْلَ طُلُوعِ الشَّمْسِ وَقَبْلَ غُرُوبِهَا}) ''isliye apney Rab ki hamd bayan kar, Suraj tulu honey se pehley aur uskey ghuroob honey se pehley.''"
4730,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke logon ne puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya qiyamat ke roz ham apney Shan Wale Rab ko dekhen gey? aapney farmaya : ''bhala aen do-pehar ke waqt , jab fiza mein koi badal waghera na ho, tumhen Suraj ke dekhney mein koi uljhan ya mushkil hoti hai?'' unhoney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''kya tumhen chaudahwin ki raat mein , jab koi badal waghaira na ho, chaand ke dekhney mein koi diqqat hoti hai? '' unhoney kaha : nahin. aapney farmaya : ''qasam us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! tumhen uskey dekhney mein koi diqqat aur mushkil nahin hogi magar itni hi jitni chaand ya Suraj ke dekhney mein hoti hai.'' (koi mushkil nahin hogi.)"
4731,"Hazrat Abu-Rizeen ( Laqeet bin Aamir ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham sab apney Rab ko dekhengey ? Ubaidullah bin Muaz ke alfaz hain : kya ham sab qiyamat ke roz usey alag alag dekhengey , to makhluq mein uski kya alamat hai? aapney farmaya : ''aey Abu-Rizeen ! kya tum mein se her koi chaand ko nahin dekhta hai?'' ibne Muaz ke alfaz hain : ''kya chaudahwin ki raat ko har koi usey akeley akeley nahin dekhta hai?'' . . . . phir dono raawiyon ka ittifaq hai. maine kaha : kyon nahin (usko dekhney mein diqqat ya azdahaam nahin hota). aapney farmaya : ''ye tu Allah ki shaan bahut buland hai.'' ibne Muaz ke alfaz hain, aapney farmaya : ''ye tu Allah ki eik makhluq ka haal hai aur Allah ki shaan be-inteha buland hai.''"
4732,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qiyamat ke din Allah taala aasmano ko lapet lega aur unhen apney dahiney haath mein lega aur kahega : main hi badshah hun. kahan hain Jabir ? kahan hain takabbur karney waley? phir zameenon ko lapet lega aur unhen pakdey ga . ibne-Al-Ula ne kaha : unhen doosrey haath mein pakdey ga aur farmaeyga : main hi badshah hun. kahan hain Jabir ? kahan hain takabbur karney waley?''"
4733,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har raat jab uska aakhiri tihai hissey baqi hota hai to hamara Rab taala aasmane duniya ki taraf utarta hai aur nidaa (awaaz) deta hai : kon hai jo mujhey pukarey , main uski sunoon aur qubul karun? kon hai jo mujh se maangey aur main usko ata karun? kon hai jo mujh se bakhshish talab karey aur main usko bakhsh dun?''"
4734,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke) ibtadaaey nabuwat ke dino mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maidane Arafat mein apney aap ko logon ke samney pesh kartey they aur kehtey they : ''suno ! koi mujhey apni qom ki taraf ley jaey, bila-shuba Quraish ne mujhey apney Rab ka kalam pahunchaney se rok diya hai.''"
4735,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke main apney aap ko is baat se bahut heech samajhti thi ke Shan Wala Allah  mere baree hone ke silsiley mein koi aisa kalam farmaeyga jiski tilawat ki jaeygi.
4736,"Janab Aamir bin Shehar (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kiya, unhoney kaha ke main Najashi ke darbar mein tha ke uskey bete ne injeel ki eik aayat padhi , main hans pada . to usney kaha : kya tum Allah taala ke kalam se hanstay ho?"
4737,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hazraat Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko in alfaz se dam kiya kartey they (أعيذ كما بكلمات الله التامة من كل شيطان وهامة ومن كل عين لامة) ''main tum dono ko Allah ke kamil kalimaat ki panah mein deta hun ke har shaitan , har moozi aur har bad-nazar ke shar se mehfooz raho.'' phir farmatey : '' tumharey abba ( Saiyedna Ibrahim Alehissalam ( Hazrat Ismail aur Is'haq (Alaihimussalaam) ko inke zariey se panah diya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye daleel hai ke Quran karim makhluq nahin."
4738,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Shan wala Allah kisi wahi ka kalam farmata hai to aasman waley aasman main eik aawaz suntey hain jaisey patthar par zanjeer ghaseeti ja rahi ho, is se wo be-hosh ho jatey hain aur phir usi kaiyfiyat mein rehtey hain yahan tak ke unke paas Jibrael aatey hain, unke aaney se unke dilon se ye kaiyfiyat zaayel (khatm) ho jati hai aur wo Jibrael se poochhtey hain : tumharey Rab ne kya farmaya? wo kehtey hain : haq farmaya. to wo bhi kehtey hain : haq farmaya , haq farmaya.''"
4739,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri sifarish meri ummat ke un logon ke liye hogi jo kabeera (badey) gunahon ke murtakib (mujrim) huey hongey.''
4740,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik giroh jahannam mein se Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki shafaat se niklega aur wo jannat mein dakhil hongey aur unka naam (jahannamin) hoga.''"
4741,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : ''bila-shuba ehle jannat , jannat mein khaeyngey aur piyeingey .''"
4742,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Soor eik seeng hai jis mein phunk maari jaeygi.''"
4743,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ibne-Adam ke sarey jism ko mitti kha jaeygi magar dam ki jad ka aakhiri hissey bacha rahega. usi se paidaish ki ibtida (shuruat) hoti hai aur usi se dobara jism murakkab (mukammal) hongey .''
4744,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Shan Wale Allah ne jannat ko paida kiya to Jibrael ameen se kaha : jao aur usey dekho . chunanche wo gaey aur usey dekha, phir aaye to kaha : aey merey Rab ! teri izzat ki qasam ! iskey mutalliq jo koi bhi suney-ga ismein dakhil hona chaheyga. phir Allah ne isko makroohaat ke gherey mein dey diya.'' (is mein aaney walon ko jo amal karney hongey aur jin sharaee paabandiyon ko qubul karna hoga , umoomi taur par unki taraf tabiyat maael nahin hoti ya haq ki raah par jamey rehney ki wajeh se takleefen uthaani hongi). phir farmaya : Jibrael ! jao aur usey dekh kar aao. isliye wo gaey aur usko dekha . phir aaye aur kaha : aey merey Rab ! teri izzat ki qasam ! mujhey andesha hai ke us mein koi dakhil nahin ho sakega . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' phir jab dozakh ko paida kiya to Jibrael se kaha : jao aur dozakh ko dekh kar aao. wo gaey aur dekh kar aaye . wapis aa kar kaha : aey merey Rab ! teri izzat ki qasam ! koi nahin jo iskey mutalliq suney aur phir is mein dakhil ho. phir Allah taala ne usko nafsani khaahishat aur marghoobaat ke gherey mein dey diya. phir farmaya : aey Jibrael ! jao aur usey dekh kar aao . wo gaey aur usey dekha . phir aaye aur kaha : aey merey Rab ! teri izzat aur terey jalal ki qasam ! mujhey andesha hai ke us mein dakhil honey se koi bhi nahin bach sakega.''"
4745,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba tumharey aagey (mehshar mein) eik hoz hai. uskey kinarey is qadr lambey hain jaisey jarbaa aur azrah ke beech fasla hai. ( ye ilaaqa Shaam ke do maqam hain inke darmiyan puraney zamaney mein teen raaton ke safar ka fasla tha.)"
4746,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. ham ne eik manzil par padaaw kiya to aapney farmaya : ''tum log merey paas hoz par aaney waley logon ka laakhwaan hissey bhi nahin ho. Abu-Hamza kehtey hain, maine puchha : usdin aap logon ki tadaad kya thi ? kaha : saat , aath sau."
4747,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ungh aa-gaee. phir aapney muskuraatey huey apna sar uthaya . aapney Sahaba se kaha, ya Sahaba ne aap se puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap kyon muskuraaey hain? farmaya : ''mujh par abhi abhi eik surat nazil hui hai.'' to aapney padha :({ بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ . . . . إِنَّا أَعْطَيْنَاكَ الْكَوْثَرَ . . . }) aakhir tak . jab aapney isey padh liya to farmaya : ''kya jantey ho kausar kya hai?'' Sahaba ne kaha : Allah aur uska Rasool behtar jantey hain. aapney farmaya : ''ye eik nehar hai jo merey Shan Wale Rab ne mujhey jannat mein deney ka wada farmaya hai aur is par khair zayada hogi , is par eik hauz hoga jis par qiyamat ke roz meri ummat ke log aaeyngey , iskey peeney ke bartan ( piyaley ( sitaron ki tadaad mein hongey.''"
4748,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke jab Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Mairaj ke moqe par jannat mein ley jaya gaya to aap ko eik nehar dikhlaai gaee jiskey kinarey aisey yaqoot ke they ke jo khaul-daar they. to wo farishta jo aap ke sath tha usney (is ki tahiya (teh) mein) haath maara aur kastoori nikali. to Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us farishtey se puchha : ''ye kya hai? '' usney kaha : ye wo kausar hai jo Shan wale Allah ne aap ko di hai.
4749,"Muslim bin Ibrahim ne bayan kiya ke hamein Abdussalam bin Abu-Haazim Abu-Taaloot ne bayan kiya aur kaha ke maine Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo (Yazid bin Muawiya ki janib se koofa ke ameer) Ubaidullah bin Ziyad ke paas gaey. Abdussalam ne kaha : mujhey eik shakhs ne bayan kiya jo us majlis mein shareek tha. (Abu-Dawud kehtey hain) Muslim bin Ibrahim ne uska naam bhi liya tha. Ubaidullah ne jab Abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha to bola : apney is motey thigney Muhammadi ko dekho . shaikh uski baat samajh gaey (ke usney taana diya hai) to unhoney kaha : mujhey ye umeed nahin thi ke main us qom mein baqi rahunga jo mujhey Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sahibiyat par taana deygi. to Ubaidullah ne un se kaha : bila-shuba Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat tumharey liye baaise izzat hai. is mein koi aeb ki baat nahin hai. phir kaha : maine aap ko isliye bula bheja hai ke aap se hauz ke mutalliq daryaft karun. kya aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko is baarey mein kuchh kehtey suna hai? to Hazrat abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : haan . koi eik , do , teen , chaar ya paanch baar nahin (balke kaee bar suna hai). to jo usko jhutlaey Allah usko us se na pilwaaey , phir ghussay se bahir nikal aaye."
4750,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman se jab qabr mein sawal kiya jata hai to wo shahadat deta hai ke eik Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain. aur yehi misdaaq (barabar) hai Shan Wale Allah is farman ka ( يُثَبِّتُ اللَّهُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا بِالْقَوْلِ الثَّابِتِ فِي الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ ) ''Allah taala ahle-eman ko pukhta baat ke sath duniya mein Sabit qadam rakhta hai aur aakhirat mein bhi Sabit qadam rakhega.''"
4751,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bano Najaar ke eik nakhlistan mein dakhil huey . aapney eik aawaz suni aur ghabra gaey aur puchha : ''ye qabron waley kon hain?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kuchh log they jo daure jahiliyat mein mar gaey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah se aag ke azab aur dajjaal ke fitney se aman maango.'' unhoney kaha : aur ye kaisey hai aey Allah ke Rasool? aapney farmaya : ''bila-shuba momin aadmi ko jab qabr mein rakha jata hai to uskey paas farishta aata hai, wo us se poochhtey hai to kis ki ibadat karta tha? to agar Allah taala usey tofiq dey , to wo kehta hai : main Allah ki ibadat kiya karta tha. phir us se puchha jata hai, to us aadmi ke baarey mein kya kaha karta tha? to wo kehta hai : ye Allah ke bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. to us se iskey alawa kuchh aur nahin puchha jata . chunanche usey eik ghar ki taraf ley jaya jata hai jo uskey liye dozakh mein muqarrar tha aur us se kaha jata hai : (dekh) dozakh mein ye tera ghar tha lekin Allah ne tujh ko bacha liya hai aur tujh par rehem kiya hai aur iskey badley tujhey jannat mein ghar dey diya hai. to wo kehta hai : mujhey chhodo ke jaun aur apney ghar walon ko khushkhabri dey aaun , to usey kaha jata hai aaram karo . aur kafir aadmi ko jab qabr mein rakha jata hai to uskey paas farishta aata hai aur usko jhidakta hai aur poochhta hai : to kis ki ibadat kiya karta tha? wo kehta hai : mujhey nahin maloom. phir usse kaha jata hai : na to ne jana aur na padha. phir us-se puchha jata hai : to us aadmi ke baarey mein kya kaha karta tha? wo jawab deta hai : main wohi kehta tha jo log kehtey they. to wo farishta lohey ke eik bhari bharkam hathodey (gurz) ke sath uskey kanon ke darmiyan maarta hai to wo us-se is qadr cheekhta chiliata hai ke jinnon aur insanon ke alawa sari makhluq uski aawaz sunti hai.''"
4752,"Muhammad bin Sulaiman ne Abdul-Wahaab se usi asnaad se is hadees ki manind riwayat kiya, kaha : ''jab bandey ko uski qabr mein rakha jata hai aur uskey sathi wapis aaney lagtey hain to wo unke qadmon ki aahat sunta hai aur uskey paas do farishtey aatey hain aur us se kehtey hain. . . .' aur pehli hadees ke qarib qarib bayan kiya. ismein kaha : ''kafir aur munafiq kehtey hain. . . .'' is mein ''munafiq'' ka lafz ziyada hai. isi ke sath ye kaha : ''uski cheekh ko jinnon aur insanon ke alawa qarib qarib ki sab makhluq sunti hai.''"
4753,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik Ansari ke janaazey mein gaey . ham qabr ke paas pahunchey to abhi lahad tayyar nahin hui thi , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) baith-gaey aur ham bhi aap ke ird-gird baith-gaey . goya ke hamarey saron par parindey hon (nihayat pursukoon aur khamoshi se baithey they). aap ke haath mein chhadi thi , aap us se zameen kured rahey they. aapney apna sar uthaya aur farmaya : ''Allah se qabr ke azab ki amaan maango.'' aapney ye do ya teen baar farmaya. Jarir ki riwayat mein yahan ye izafa hai. . . ''jab log wapis jatey hain to maiyat unke qadmon ki aahat sunti hai, jabkey us-se ye puchha ja raha hota hai : aey falan ! tera Rab kon hai? tera deen kya hai? aur tera Nabi kon hai?'' Hannaad ne kaha : farmaya : ''uskey paas do farishtey aatey hain aur usey bithaatey hain aur usey kehtey hain : tera Rab kon hai? to wo kehta hai : mera Rab Allah hai. phir wo poochhtey hain : tera deen kya hai? to wo kehta hai : mera deen Islam hai. phir wo poochhtey hain : ye aadmi kon hai jo tum mein bheja gaya tha? to wo kehta hai : wo Allah ke Rasool hain. . . (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) . . phir wo kehtey hain : tujhey kaisey ilm hua? wo kehta hai : maine Allah ki kitab padhi , main uspar emaan laya aur uski tasdeeq ki.'' Jarir ki riwayat mein mazeed hai : '' yehi (sawal jawab hi) misdaaq hai Shan Wale Allah ke is farman ka ( يُثَبِّتُ اللَّهُ الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا بِالْقَوْلِ الثَّابِتِ فِي الْحَيَاةِ الدُّنْيَا وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ ) phir wo dono riwayat karney mein muttafiq hain. farmaya : ''phir aasman se manadi karney wala aelan karta hai : tehqiq merey bandey ne sach kaha hai, usey jannat ka bistar bichha do , aur usko jannat ka libas pehna do , aur uskey liye jannat ki taraf se darwaza khol do.'' farmaya : ''jannat ki taraf se wahan ki hawaeyn , raahatein aur khushbu aaney lagti hain aur uski qabr ko intihaaye nazar tak wasee kar diya jata hai.'' phir kafir aur uski maut ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : uski rooh uskey jism mein lautaai jati hai aur wo uskey paas aatey hain aur usey bithaatey hain aur us-se poochhtey hain : tera Rab kon hai? to wo kehta hai : ha ! ha ! mujhey khabar nahin. phir wo us-se poochhtey hain : tera deen kya hai? to wo kehta hai :ha ! ha ! mujhey khabar nahin. phir wo us-se poochhtey hain : ye aadmi kon hai jo tum mein bheja gaya tha? to wo kehta hai : ha ! ha ! mujhey khabar nahin. to manadi aasman se nidaa (awaaz) deta hai ke usney jhoot kaha, usey aag ka bistar bichha do , usey aag ka libas pehna do aur uskey liye dozakh ki taraf se darwaza khol do . farmaya ke phir us jahannam ki taraf se uski tapish aur sakht garm hawa aaney lagti hai aur uspar qabr ko tang kar diya jata hai yahan tak ke uski pasliyan eik doosre mein ghus jati hain.'' Jarir ki riwayat mein mazeed hai : ''phir us-par eik andha gunga farishta muqarrar kar diya jata hai, jiskey paas bhari gurz hota hai. agar usey pahad par maara jaey to wo ( pahad) mitti-mitti ho jaey. phir wo usey uskey sath aisi chot maarta hai jiski aawaz jinnon aur insanon ke alawa mashriq aur maghrib ke darmiyan sari makhluq sunti hai. aur phir wo mitti (reza reza) ho jata hai.'' farmaya : phir usmein rooh lautaai jati hai.''"
4754,Abu-Umar Azan ne kaha ke maine Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se suna . unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uski manind riwayat kiya.
4755,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney jahannam ka zikr kiya aur roney lagin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''tujhey kis chiz ne rulaayaa hai?'' kehney lagin : mujhey jahannam yaad aai hai to roney lagi hun. to kya bhala aap qiyamat ke roz apney ghar walon ko yaad rakhengey? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen maqamat aisey hain jahan koi kisi ko yaad nahin kerega : tarazu ke paas yahan tak ke usey pata chal jaey ke uska tol halka hua ya bhari, namae-aamaal milney ke waqt , jab kaha jaeyga (هاؤم اقرءوا كتابيه) ''aao mera namae-aamaal padho.'' yahan tak ke jaan ley ke uska aamaal nama uskey daain haath mein aata hai ya baeyn mein ya kamar ke peechhey sey, aur (teesra maqam) pul-siraat hai jab usey jahannam par aen beech mein tikaaya jaeyga. Yaqoob ne (Yonus se) ke alfaz se riwayat ki aur ye hadees usi ke alfaz mein hai."
4756,"Hazrat Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : '' tehqiq Nooh Alehissalam ke baad jo bhi Nabi aaya usney apni qom ko dajjaal se daraya hai aur main bhi tumhen us-se dara raha hun.'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski alaamaat bayan farmaeen aur kaha : ''mumkin hai ke usey wo aadmi pa ley jisney mujhey dekha hai aur meri baaten suni hain.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! un dino hamarey dil kaisey hongey? kya bhala aisey hi hongey jaisey ke aaj hain? farmaya : ''ya is-se behtar.''"
4757,"Janab Salim apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ko khutba deney ke liye khadey huey . aapney Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki jo uskey layaq hai. phir aapney dajjaal ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : ''main tumhen us se dara raha hun aur jo bhi Nabi aaya hai usney apni qom ko us se daraya hai. yaqinan Nooh Alehissalam ne bhi apni qom ko us se daraya tha, lekin main tumhen uskey baarey mein aisi baat keh raha hun jo kisi Nabi ne apni qom ko nahin batai . tum jaan lo ke wo kaanaa hai aur Shan Wala Allah qataee kaanaa nahin hai.''"
4758,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney jamaat se baalisht bhar bhi alehdgi ikhtiyar ki, usney Islam ki rassi ko apney galey se utaar phenka.''"
4759,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey baad tumhara kya haal hoga jabkey Imam ( khalifa ( is maale-fai aur ghanimat ko zaati maal samjhen gey.'' (yani sharae taqaazon ke mutabiq kharch aur taqseem nahin karengey.) maine arz kiya us zaat ki qasam ! jisney aap ko haq ke sath ( sachcha peghambar bana ke) bheja , tab to main apni talwaar apney kandhey par rakh lunga aur us se maarun ga yahan tak ke aap se aa miloon . aapney farmaya : ''kya main tumhen is-se behtar baat na bata dun? sabr karna yahan tak ke mujh se aa milo."
4760,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum par aisey Imam ( ameer ( muqarrar hongey jin ki kuchh baaten tumhen bhali lagengi aur kuchh buri bhi janogey. to jisney inkar kiya. . . .  Hisham ke alfaaz mein . . . . apni zaban se inkar kiya, to wo bari hua , aur jisney dil se inkar kiya wo mehfooz raha , lekin jo razi raha aur unka muttabey bana.''  kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! to kya ham unko qatl na keren? aapney farmaya : ''nahin, jab tak ke wo Namaz padhtey rahen.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha :  (أفلا نقاتلهم?) kya ham un se qitaal na karen?"
4761,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kiya. aapney farmaya : ''jisney dil se napasand jana aur makruh samjha wo bari hua aur jisney inkar kiya wo mehfooz raha.'' Qatada (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maqsad ye hai ke dil se inkar kiya aur dil se bura jana.
4762,"Hazrat Arfaja (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''meri ummat mein fitney hongey, fitney aur fitney . chunanche jisney chaha ke musalmanon ke maamley mein tafarqa (farq) dal dey jabkey wo muttahid aur muttafiq hon to aisey ko talwaar se qatl kar dena , chahey (chahen) koi bhi ho.''"
4763,"Janab Ubeda Salmaani ne riwayat kiya ke Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehle naharwaan ka tazkira kiya aur bataya ke un main eik aadmi hoga jis ka eik haath chhota hoga ya us mein nuqs hoga ya aisey hoga jaisey aurat ka pistaan, agar mujhey andesha na ho ke tum log khushi mein aa kar bahut aagey badh jaogey to main tumhen wo zarur bata deta jo Shan Wale Allah ne Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani un se qitaal karney waley ke baarey mein wada farmaya hai. Ubeda kehtey hain maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya ye farman aapney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha? farmaya : haan , Rabbe-Kaaba ki qasam !"
4764,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein kuchh sona bheja jo abhi saaf nahin kiya gaya tha. aapney usey Aqraa bin Haabis Hanzali Majaashi , Uena bin Badr Fazaari, bano Nabhan ke Zaidul Khail Taai aur bano kilaab ke Alqama bin Ulaasa Aamiree chaar aadmiyon mein taqseem kar diya. to qureshiyon aur Ansariyon ko is par ghussa aaya aur unhoney kaha : ehle-Najad ke badon ko dey rahey hain aur hamein chhod rahey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main to unke dilon ko mohna chahta hun (taake Islam mein unka dil jam jaey).'' to is beech main eik aadmi aaya jiski aankhen gahri (andar ko dhansi hui) thin rukhsaar ubhrey huye, peshani ooper ko uthi hui, dadhi ghani aur sar mundaa hua tha, kehney laga : aey Muhammad ! Allah se daro . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar mein hi Allah ki nafarmani karney lagun to kon uski itaat kerega? Shan Wala Allah to mujhey zameen walon ke liye ameen banaey aur tum mujhey ameen nahin samajhtey ho?'' raawi ne kaha : is par eik shakhs ne puchha : kya main isko qatl kar dun? mera khayal hai wo Khalid bin Waleed they. magar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey rok diya. phir jab wo kamar pher kar chala gaya to aapney farmaya : ''is shakhs ki nasal mein aisey log hongey jo Quran padhengey magar wo unke halqon se nichey nahin utreyga, Islam se aisey niklengey jaisey teer apney shikar se nikal jata hai ye log musalmanon ko qatl karengey aur but-paraston ko chhoden gey , Allah ki qasam ! agar maine unko paya to unhen qome Aad ki manind qatl karunga.''"
4765,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri aur Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat mein ikhtilaf aur iftiraaq (bhed-bhaw) aa jaeyga. eik qom baaten bahut achchhi-achchhi karegi magar kaam unke bahut burey hongey. Quran padhtey hongey magar wo unki hansliyon se nichey nahin utrey ga . wo deen se aisey nikal jaeyngey jaisey teer apney hadaf ( shikar ( se nikal jata hai. unka haq ki taraf lautna aisey hi muhaal hoga jaisey teer ka apni kamaan par wapis aana . wo insanon mein aur makhluqat mein sab se burey hongey. Mubarak ho aisey shakhs ko jo unhen qatl karey aur wo usey qatl karen. (shahadat pa jaey.) wo ba-zahir Allah ki kitab ki taraf bulaeyn gey magar unka koi talluq us kitab se nahin hoga. jo un se qitaal kerega wo unki nisbat Allah taala se bahut qarib hoga.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! unki alaamat kya hogi? aapney farmaya : ''sar mundaanaa.''"
4766,"Janab Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya hai. is riwayat mein hai : ''un (khawaarij) ki alamat sar mundaanaa aur baal door karna hai. jab tum unhen pao to unhen sulaa (qatl kar) dena. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : hadees mein waarid lafz ( التسبيد (ke maani hain (استئصال الشعر)  ''baalon ko jadon se ukhedna ya jadon se mundna.''"
4767,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees bayan karta hun ( to us mein kuchh chhupa nahin hota, bilkul haq aur saaf hoti hai) mujhey aasman se girna , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jhoot bolney ki nisbat bahut ziyada pasand hai aur jab main tum se aapas ki koi baat karta hun to (yaad rakho) ladaai chaal ka naam hai (bahut se maslihatein malhooz rakhni zaroori hain isliye un baaton ko aam nahin karna chahiye) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna aap farmatey they : ''aakhiri zamaney mein log aaeyngey jo umaron mein nau-jawan hongey magar be-aql. makhluq mein sab se afzal tareen shakhsiyat ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ki baaten kartey hongey magar deen se aisey guzar jaeyngey jaisey ke teer apney shikar se nikal jata hai. unka emaan unke halqon se nichey nahin utarta hoga. tum un se jahan bhi milo , unhen qatl kar dena . bila-shuba unke qatl mein unke qatil ke liye qiyamat ke roz bahut bada ajr hoga.''"
4768,"Zaid bin Wahab Juhni ne bayan kiya ke wo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath us lashkar mein shareek tha jo khaarjiyon ki taraf gaya tha. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : logo ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''meri ummat mein aisey log hongey jo Quran padhtey hongey . tumhari qirat unki qirat ke muqabley mein kuchh bhi nahin hogi , na tumhari namazein unki namazon ke muqabley mein kuchh hongi na tumharey rozey unke rozon ke muqabley mein kuchh haisiyat rakhtey hongey, wo Quran padhtey hongey aur samjhengey ke ye unke haq mein daleel aur taeed hai, halanke wo unke khilaf hoga. unki namazein unki hansliyon se aagey nahin badhengi. Islam se aisey guzar jaeyngey jaisey teer apney shikar mein se nikal jata hai.'' agar us lashkar ko jo un (khaarjiyon) ko qatl kerega un fazaail ka ilm ho jaey jo Allah ne unke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani unke liye muqaddar farmaai hain to wo usi par takiya kar lein aur un (khaarjiyon) ki nishani ye hai ke un main eik aisa aadmi hoga jiski kohni se ooper ka bazu to hoga , kohni se nichey kalaai nahin hogi. ooper ke bazu ka aakhir pistaan ki bhatni ki tarah hoga. us par safed baal hongey . kya bhala tum log Muawiya aur ahle-Sham ki taraf jana chahtey ho aur un (khaarjiyon) ko apni auladon aur maal aur asbab mein peechhey chhod dena chahtey ho? Allah ki qasam ! mujhey umeed hai ke yehi wo log hain. (jin ki khabar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne di) unhoney haram khoon bahaayaa aur logon ke mehfooz ilaqey ( jaan , izzat , maal ( looti. chunanche Allah ka naam lekar ( unke muqabley mein) chalo. Salma bin Kuheil ne kaha ke Zaid bin Wahab mujhey manzil b-manzil lekar chaltey gaey yahan tak ke ham eik pul se guzrey , phir bataya ke jab ham unke muqabil huey aur khaarjiyon ka sardar Abdullah bin Wahab Rasbee tha to usney apney logon se kaha : neze phenk do aur talwaarein apni miyaanon se nikal lo. mujhey dar hai ke ye tum se usi tarah muqabla karengey jaisey harooraa waley din kiya tha. kaha : chunanche un logon ne apney neze phenk diye aur talwaarein khinch lein to logon ne unko apney nezon se chhalni karna shuru kar diya aur unko eik doosrey ke ooper qatl kiya. jabkey Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke lashkar mein se sirf do aadmi Shahid huey. to Hazrat Ali ne kaha : talash karo, un main eik lunja hoga , magar unhen na mila . to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) khud uthey yahan tak ke un maiyaton ke paas aaye jo eik doosrey par qatl huey they. unhoney farmaya : inhen nikalo . chunanche unhoney usey pa liya jo ke sab se nichey zameen par pada tha. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allahu-Akbar pukara aur kaha : Allah ne sach farmaya aur uskey Rasool ne pahuncha diya. isliye Janab Ubeda Salmaani unki taraf khadey huey aur kaha : aey Ameerul-momeneen ! qasam us Allah ki jiskey siwa koi mabud nahin ! kya ye bayan aapney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha? unhoney farmaya : haan Allah ki qasam ! jiskey siwa koi mabud nahin. yahan tak ke unhoney teen baar qasam di aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi teen baar qasam se jawab diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Imam Maalik ne farmaya : ye ilm ki ihaanat hai ke aalim her poochhney waley ka jawab deney lagey."
4769,"Abu-Wazee ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : us lunje ko talash karo . aur hadees bayan ki . chunanche usey maqtooleen ke nichey se nikal liya gaya jo keechad mein lat pat pada tha. Abu-Wazee ne kaha : main goya usey dekh raha hun, Habshi aadmi tha, us par qubaa thi , uska eik haath aisey tha jaisey aurat ki pistaan par bhatni . uspar chand baal they jaisey jangli choohey ki dam par hotey hain."
4770,"Abu-Maryam ne kaha : tehqiq ye lunja aadmi un dino hamarey sath masjid mein hota tha. din raat ham uskey sath baithtey they, faqeer aadmi tha. maine usey miskeenon ke sath dekha jo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke tuaam (khane) mein shareek hota tha, jo wo logon ke sath tanaawul (khaya) kartey they. aur maine usko apna over-coat bhi diya tha. Abu-Maryam ne kaha : us lunje ko (نافع ذوالثدية) ( pistaan wala ( kaha jata tha. uskey bazu par aurat ke pistaan ki tarah pistaan sa tha aur uskey sirey par bhatni bhi thi. aur us par billi ki moonchhon ki tarah kuchh baal they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : logon mein uska naam Harqoos maroof hai."
4771,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis kisi ka maal nahaq taur par chheenney ki koshish ki gaee aur phir usney qitaal kiya aur us mein wo qatl ho gaya , to wo Shaheed hai.''"
4772,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney maal ki hifazat mein qatl ho jaey wo Shahid hai. aur jo apney ghar walon ki hifazat ya khoon ya deen ke difaa mein qatl ho jaey, wo Shahid hai."
